%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Brace%20for%20wild%20swings%20in%20US%20stocks%20amid%20elevated%20interest-rate%20uncertainty%2C%20wealth%20manager%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227029%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22stock%20market%20traders%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F646be8fd2e229f0018269668%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225272%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EExpect%20stock%20volatility%20in%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20says%20David%20Donabedian%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%20of%20CIBC%20Private%20Wealth%20US.%3Cp%3EANGELA%20WEISS%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EUS%20stocks%20just%20had%20their%20best%20week%20in%20a%20year%2C%20but%20don't%20expect%20the%20upbeat%20trend%20to%20last.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20market%20could%20face%20wild%20swings%20into%20year-end%20due%20to%20uncertainty%20over%20interest%20rates%2C%20said%20CIBC%20Private%20Wealth's%20David%20Donabedian.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20last%20week%20was%20a%20good%20one%20for%20the%20equity%20market%2C%20it%20will%20not%20always%20be%20that%20easy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20stocks%20just%20had%20their%20best%20week%20in%20a%20year.%20But%20don't%20take%20that%20to%20mean%20a%20smooth%20ride%20ahead%2C%20according%20to%20one%20expert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPersistent%20uncertainty%20about%20the%20future%20direction%20of%20interest%20rates%20will%20fuel%20increased%20volatility%20in%20equities%20in%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20according%20to%20David%20Donabedian%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%20of%20CIBC%20Private%20Wealth%20US%2C%20which%20oversees%20more%20than%20%24100%20billion%20in%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20benchmark%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20index%20of%20US%20shares%20jumped%205.85%25%20last%20week%2C%20after%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20left%20interest%20rates%20unchanged%20for%20the%20second%20straight%20policy%20meeting.%20Softer-than-expected%20jobs%20data%20also%20fueled%20expectations%20the%20central%20bank%20will%20refrain%20from%20further%20increases%20in%20borrowing%20costs%20as%20the%20economy%20starts%20slowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20improved%20sentiment%20in%20equities%20saw%20the%20market's%20so-called%20fear%20gauge%2C%20the%20CBOE%20Volatility%20Index%20or%20VIX%2C%20plunge%20the%20most%20since%202021%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20decline%20in%20the%20uncertainty%20gauge%20could%20prove%20temporary%2C%20going%20by%20Donabedian's%20outlook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20last%20week%20was%20a%20good%20one%20for%20the%20equity%20market%2C%20it%20will%20not%20always%20be%20that%20easy.%20We%20expect%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20year%20to%20be%20volatile%2C%20going%20through%20manic%20depressive%20swings%20based%20on%20where%20interest%20rates%20are%20headed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20emailed%C2%A0%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20reason%20for%20such%20volatility%20would%20be%20the%20unresolved%20uncertainty%20over%20interest%20rates%2C%20he%20said.%20While%20it%20hasn't%20raised%20borrowing%20costs%20since%20July%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20is%20still%20maintaining%20its%20stance%20that%20rates%20will%20remain%20higher%20for%20longer%2C%20given%20the%20lingering%20threat%20of%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLooking%20ahead%2C%20however%2C%20there%20may%20be%20a%20reality%20check%20ahead%20on%20the%20Fed.%20If%20bond%20yields%20continue%20to%20fall%2C%20will%20a%20rate%20hike%20be%20back%20on%20the%20table%3F%20We%20need%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Donabedian%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20stocks%20have%20been%20taking%20cues%20in%20recent%20months%20from%20the%20Treasury%20bond%20market%2C%20where%20benchmark%20yields%20hit%2016-year%20highs%20above%205%25%20in%20late%20October.%20Higher%20yields%20on%20government%20bonds%2C%20which%20are%20considered%20a%20safer%20form%20of%20investment%2C%20tend%20to%20lure%20investors%20away%20from%20riskier%20assets%20such%20as%20equities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fed%20has%20raised%20its%20benchmark%20rate%20by%20more%20than%20500%20basis%20points%20since%20early%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-sp500-brace-for-wild-swings-expert-says-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699356209000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F646be8fd2e229f0018269668%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-sp500-brace-for-wild-swings-expert-says-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20stocks%20had%20their%20best%20week%20in%20a%20year%2C%20but%20optimism%20may%20not%20last.%20Brace%20for%20%26quot%3Bmanic%20depressive%20swings%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20CIBC%20Private%20Wealth's%20David%20Donabedian.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22avarma%40insider.com%20(Anil%20Varma)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-sp500-brace-for-wild-swings-expert-says-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20%7C%20As%20Israel%20Escalates%20Attacks%20on%20Gaza%2C%20Has%20Blinken%E2%80%99s%20Diplomacy%20Failed%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07162541%2FKT-7-Nov-2023-B.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EKaran%20Thapar%20interviews%20Hanan%20Ashrawi%2C%20former%20higher%20education%20minister%20in%20the%20Palestine%20Authority%20who%20won%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Peace%20Prize%20in%202005%2C%20who%20assesses%20the%20impact%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20escalating%20attacks%20on%20Gaza%20and%20US%20secretary%20of%20state%20Antony%20Blinken%E2%80%99s%20shuttle%20diplomacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20the%20true%20outcome%20of%20Blinken%E2%80%99s%20frantic%20ef