diatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fbeijing-confirms-chinese-casualties-in-myanmar-clashes%2Farticleshow%2F105039619.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fbeijing-confirms-chinese-casualties-in-myanmar-clashes%2Famp_articleshow%2F105039619.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fbeijing-confirms-chinese-casualties-in-myanmar-clashes%2Famp_articleshow%2F105039619.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%20Caste%20Survey%3A%20The%20Who%E2%80%99s%20Who%20in%20the%20Data%20%7C%20Nai%2FHajjaam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07150202%2F6014608342_59791f2722_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBeyond%20politics%2C%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20is%20a%20revolutionary%20document.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20public%20document%2C%20the%20first%20ever%20after%201931%2C%20allowing%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Nai%20or%20Hajjaam%20(2%2C082%2C048%20people)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECastes%20are%20not%20mere%20classification%20of%20the%20basis%20of%20labour.%20In%20western%20countries%2C%20members%20of%20the%20same%20family%20can%20opt%20for%20different%20professions%20and%20a%20single%20family%20can%20have%20cattle%20herders%2C%20carpenters%20and%20cobblers%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20But%20it%20is%20not%20so%20under%20the%20caste%20system.%20When%20professions%20are%20segregated%20into%20castes%2C%20social%20rules%20are%20imposed%20accordingly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20of%20the%20caste%20group%20we%20are%20talking%20about%20today%20can%20be%20found%20anywhere%2C%20be%20it%20a%20city%20or%20a%20village.%20They%20can%20be%20Hindu%20or%20Muslim.%20Among%20Muslims%20they%20are%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHajjaam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20the%20work%20done%20by%20them%20is%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ehajamat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20There%20are%20several%20names%20for%20them%20among%20Hindus%2C%20such%20as%20Nau%2C%20Naua%2C%20Kshaurik%2C%20Napit%2C%20Mundak%2C%20Bhandik%2C%20Nais%2C%20Sain%2C%20Sen%2C%20Savita-Samaj%2C%20Mangala%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20425px)%2085vw%2C%20425px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22425%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22609%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20caste%20group%20also%20has%20various%20names%20in%20different%20states.%20In%20Punjab%2C%20they%20are%20sometimes%20affectionately%20called%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3Eraja%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fi%3Eor%20king.%20They%20are%20called%20Kulin%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Khawas%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Sen%20Samaj%20or%20Napit%20in%20Haryana%2C%20and%20Nai-Thakur%20or%20Savita%20Samaj%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20are%20responsible%20for%20cutting%20hair%20and%20grooming%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Bihar%2C%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20are%20considered%20extremely%20backward.%20According%20to%20the%20caste-based%20survey%20report%20released%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%2C%20their%20population%20in%20Bihar%20is%202%2C082%2C048%2C%20which%20is%20only%201.5927%25%20in%20terms%20of%20share.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Yet%2C%20this%20caste%20group%20has%20a%20special%20role%20in%20society%20and%20politics.%20As%20far%20as%20their%20social%20status%20is%20concerned%2C%20they%20are%20present%20in%20all%20important%20rituals%20in%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20life%2C%20from%20birth%20to%20death%2C%20along%20with%20people%20of%20the%20Brahmin%20caste.%20But%20they%20are%20not%20given%20the%20same%20respect%20as%20the%20Brahmins.%20In%20north%20India%2C%20there%20is%20a%20saying%20which%20derogatorily%20equates%20the%20Nai%20with%20a%20crow%20%E2%80%93%20a%20clever%20omnivorous%20bird.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20they%20are%20not%20untouchable%20because%20declaring%20them%20as%20such%20would%20cause%20discomfort%20to%20the%20people%20of%20this%20society%20who%20avail%20themselves%20of%20the%20services%20of%20this%20caste.%20Moreover%2C%20if%20someone%20wants%20to%20get%20shaved%2C%20they%20must%20allow%20the%20barber%20to%20touch%20their%20face.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20discussion%20in%20the%20Atharva%20Ved%20about%20%E2%80%9Cmaking%20them%20touchable.%E2%80%9D%20A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eshloka%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Esays%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20main%20person%20in%20the%20marriage%20ceremony%20is%20the%20barber%2C%20who%20finds%20a%20groom%20for%20the%20girl%20and%20verifies%20his%20qualifications.%20They%20perform%20key%20rituals%20and%20that%20is%20why%20they%20are%20the%20first%20ones%20to%20be%20entitled%20to%20wear%20Panchavastra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20biggest%20contradiction%20in%20Indian%20society%20is%20that%20this%20essential%20labour%20too%20has%20been%20devalued.%20But%20if%20we%20look%20at%20the%20history%20of%20the%20development%20of%20human%20civilisation%2C%20perhaps%20the%20barber%20was%20the%20first%20person%20to%20have%20thought%20of%20grooming%20a%20person%20to%20make%20them%20look%20beautiful.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Historically%2C%20the%20period%20of%20emergence%20of%20barbers%20must%20have%20been%20after%20the%20Neolithic%20era%20when%20iron%20was%20discovered%20because%20scissors%20and%20other%20tools%20would%20not%20exist%20without%20iron.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20role%20of%20the%20barber%20community%20cannot%20be%20dismissed%20in%20the%20development%20of%20human%20civilisation.%20He%20was%20the%20first%20surgeon%20who%20used%20his%20tools%20to%20remove%20thorns%20from%20the%20feet%20of%20countless%20people%20and%20healed%20their%20wounds.%20Be%20it%20a%20king%20or%20a%20common%20man%2C%20barbers%20have%20served%20everyone%2C%20across%20caste%20groups%20too.%20Even%20today%2C%20in%20the%20villages%20of%20Bihar%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20women%20of%20the%20barber%20community%20serve%20women%20of%20all%20other%20castes%20%E2%80%93%20they%20clip%20nails%20and%20apply%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ealta%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20their%20feet%2C%20among%20other%20things.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20their%20wages%20were%20called%20%3Cem%3Ej%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Eajmanaka%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20They%20had%20a%20fixed%20share%20in%20every%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20household%20%E2%80%93%20one%20or%20two%20sacks%20of%20grains.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20despite%20being%20landless%2C%20the%20people%20of%20the%20barber%20community%20always%20had%20full%20barns.%20But%20now%20the%20era%20of%20j%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eajmanaka%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20gone.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20do%20business%20in%20cash%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKarpoori%20Thakur%2C%20from%20the%20community%2C%20was%20a%20renowned%20politician%20of%20Bihar%20who%20became%20its%20chief%20minister%20twice.%20The%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Mungerilal%20Commission%20implemented%20by%20him%20gave%20an%20impetus%20to%20the%20politics%20of%20backward%20classes%20in%20the%20country.%20However%2C%20at%20present%2C%20it%20seems%20this%20community%20is%20in%20search%20of%20a%20hero%20for%20itself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F260208%2Fbihar-caste-survey-what-is-the-history-of-chaupal-caste%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3EGhasi%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3ESantrash%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3EMadaria%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-koeri-kushwaha%5C%22%3EKoeri%2FKushwaha%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chaupal%5C%22%3EChaupal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20series%20is%20available%20in%20Hindi%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F260200%2Fbihar-caste-survey-who-are-the-santarash%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20in%20Urdu%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewireurdu.com%2Fauthor%2Fnaval-kishor-kumar%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%