Cp%3EThe%20strong%20remarks%20by%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Sanjay%20Kishan%20Kaul%20and%20Justice%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20came%20during%20a%20hearing%20on%20a%20petition%20by%20Foundation%20for%20Media%20Professionals%2C%20which%20has%20sought%20detailed%20guidelines%20for%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20seizing%20journalists'%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20serious%20matter.%20There%20should%20be%20better%20guidlines%20for%20media%20professionals.%20Media%20professionals%20have%20their%20own%20sources.%20We%20have%20held%20right%20to%20privacy%20a%20fundamental%20right.%20There%20should%20be%20a%20balance%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%20The%20matter%20will%20be%20heard%20next%20on%20December%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20given%20time%20to%20centre%20to%20prepare%20such%20guidelines.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Centre%20should%20prepare%20the%20guidelines.%20If%20you%20want%2C%20we%20will%20do%20it.%20But%20I%20think%20you%20should%20do%20it.%20This%20cannot%20be%20a%20State%20that's%20run%20through%20its%20agencies%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Kaul%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Solicitor%20General%20SV%20Raju%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Centre%2C%20said%20the%20matter%20before%20the%20court%20relates%20to%20complex%20legal%20issues.%20%26quot%3BThe%20media%20has%20rights%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20above%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20counsel%20for%20the%20petitioner%20said%20this%20matter%20is%20about%20%26quot%3BState%20power%20vs%20self%20incrimination%2C%20privacy%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BNowdays%20they%20compel%20to%20share%20passwords%20or%20biometrics.There%20are%20no%20guidelines%20with%20respect%20to%20when%20they%20will%20seize%2C%20what%20they%20will%20seize%2C%20personal%20data%2C%20financial%20data%20all%20digital%20footprint%20is%20on%20that%20device%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20counsel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20stressed%20that%20the%20Centre%20must%20analyse%20what%20kind%20of%20guidelines%20are%20needed%20in%20this%20case.%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20like%20ASG%20to%20work%20on%20this%20and%20come%20back%20on%20this%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20as%20many%20as%2016%20press%20freedom%20organisations%20had%20written%20to%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20seeking%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20intervention%20to%20end%20the%20alleged%20%26quot%3Brepressive%26quot%3B%20use%20of%20investigating%20agencies%20against%20the%20media.%20They%20had%20sought%20guidelines%20on%20police%20seizing%20electronic%20devices%20of%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20had%20come%20after%20Delhi%20Police%20raided%20the%20homes%20of%20journalists%2C%20editors%20and%20writers%20associated%20with%20the%20news%20portal%20'Newsclick'.%20NewsClick%20founder%20founder%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20its%20Human%20Resources%20head%20Amit%20Chakravarty%20have%20been%20arrested%20under%20anti-terror%20law%20UAPA.%20The%20web%20portal%2C%20it%20is%20alleged%2C%20received%20money%20to%20spread%20pro-China%20propaganda.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20raids%20on%20premises%20linked%20to%20NewsClick%20and%20its%20contributors%2C%20press%20freedom%20organisations%20had%20flagged%20how%20phones%20and%20computers%20were%20seized%20without%20ensuring%20data%20integrity.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699353600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-06%2Fmedia-generic-istock_650x400_61496842801.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-be-state-run-by-agencies-supreme-court-bats-for-press-freedom-4553806%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mediapersons%20have%20their%20sources%20for%20gathering%20news%20and%20the%20centre%20should%20prepare%20separate%20guidelines%20for%20the%20seizure%20of%20journalists'%20digital%20equipment%20for%20any%20investigation%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-be-state-run-by-agencies-supreme-court-bats-for-press-freedom-4553806%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-be-state-run-by-agencies-supreme-court-bats-for-press-freedom-4553806%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-be-state-run-by-agencies-supreme-court-bats-for-press-freedom-4553806%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Analysis%3A%20Relationship%20Status%20Of%20BJP%2C%20Pawan%20Kalyan%2C%20C%20Naidu%20-%20Complicated%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPawan%20Kalyan%20makes%20a%20public%20appearance%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20Hyderabad%20and%20the%20BJP%20allots%20eight%20seats%20to%20his%20Jana%20Sena%20in%20Telangana.%20This%2C%20when%20the%20actor-politician%20is%20already%20electorally%20committed%20to%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20has%20declared%20that%20the%20two%20will%20join%20hands%20to%20defeat%20their%20bete%20noire%20YS%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20not%20willing%20to%20consider%20friendship%20with%20Naidu's%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20and%20has%20been%20cold%20to%20its%20overtures.%20The%20BJP-JSP-TDP%20relationship%20status%20-%20complicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20cinematic%20style%2C%20Jana%20Sena%20chief%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20declared%20outside%20Rajamahendravaram%20Central%20Jail%20on%20September%2014%20that%20come%20what%20may%2C%20his%20party%20and%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20would%20fight%20together%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20in%20the%202024%20election.%20In%20the%20same%20breath%2C%20he%20said%20he%20remained%20a%20part%20of%20the%20NDA%20and%20that%20he%20and%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20were%20already%20committed%20to%20the%20BJP%20as%20part%20of%20the%20alliance.%20He%20has%20repeatedly%20said%20he%20hopes%20all%20three%20can%20come%20together%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20to%20defeat%20Jagan%20Reddy's%20YSRCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20relationship%20history%20with%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20does%20not%20make%20it%20easy%20for%20them%20to%20forget%20the%20past%20and%20consent%20to%20a%20cosy%20threesome%20with%20the%20TDP%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20like%20in%202014.%20The%20BJP%20is%20not%20ready%20for%20a%20reconciliation%20after%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20walked%20out%20on%20the%20party%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20action%20for%20now%20has%20moved%20to%20neighbouring%20Telangana%2C%20where%20elections%20are%20due%20in%20about%20three%20weeks.%20The%20umbilical%20connection%20between%20the%20two%20Telugu%20states%20means%20politics%20in%20the%20two%20states%20is%20deeply%20intertwined.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20TDP%2C%20which%20was%20in%20a%20pre-poll%20People's%20Alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20in%202018%2C%20has%20declared%20that%20the%20bicycle%20(TDP's%20symbol)%20won't%20participate%20in%20the%20Telangana%20election.%20Though%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20is%20in%20Hyderabad%20-%20he%20was%20granted%20bail%20for%20medical%20treatment%20-%20he%20prefers%20to%20invest%20his%20time%20and%20resources%20on%20the%20fight%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20has%20opted%20out%20of%20the%20poll%20battle%20in%20Telangana.%20So%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%2040%20years%2C%20the%20bicycle%20will%20be%20missing%20from%20the%20ballot%20in%20any%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20own%20political%20graph%20in%20Telangana%2C%20seen%20to%20have%20soared%20since%202020%2C%20has%20fallen%20after%20its%20inexplicable%20decision%20to%20replace%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20as%20state%20chief%2C%20and%20apparent%20reluctance%20to%20act%20against%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20(KCR's)%20daughter%20K%20Kavitha.%20So%20the%20BJP%20is%20perceived%20to%20have%20lost%20the%20anti-KCR%20sentiment%20votes%20to%20the%20Congress.%20The%20party%20would%20like%20to%20limit%20the%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20where%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20comes%20in.%20For%20all%20the%20crowds%20that%20he%20draws%20and%20the%20hype%2C%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20has%20not%20really%20set%20the%20electoral%20box%20office%20on%20fire.%20He%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20win%20from%20either%20of%20the%20two%20assembly%20seats%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20that%20he%20contested%20in%202019.%20The%20Jana%20Sena%20won%20a%20single%20assembly%20seat%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20the%20BJP%20keen%20on%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20in%20Telangana%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%2C%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20has%20not%20been%20politically%20active%20in%20Telangana%20but%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20the%20actor%20has%20his%20fans%2C%20especially%20among%20the%20youth%20across%20the%20two%20Telugu%20states.%20So%2C%20his%20star%20appeal%20can%20bring%20in%20some%20votes%20for%20the%20BJP%20at%20a%20time%20their%20political%20prospects%20are%20looking%20bleak%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20KCR's%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20is%20admittedly%20on%20the%20backfoot%20with%20the%20youth%20with%20perception%20gaining%20ground%20about%20Telangana's%20ruling%20party%20not%20doing%20enough%20for%20jobs%20and%20unemployment%2C%20the%20youth%20are%20a%20segment%20whose%20vote%20could%20otherwise%20go%20to%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%2C%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20brother%2C%20megastar%20Chiranjeevi%2C%20had%20managed%20an%20impressive%2018%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20vote%20share%20in%202009%20in%20the%20Praja%20Rajyam's%20debut%20electoral%20outing%2C%20not%20just%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20his%20larger-than-life%20star%20appeal%20but%20also%20the%20social%20justice%20plank%20and%20the%20Backward%20Caste%20Munnuru%20Kapu%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20meeting%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20where%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20is%20special%20guest%2C%20focuses%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bself-respect%26quot%3B%20of%20Backward%20Caste%20communities.%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20announced%20that%20if%20Telangana%20votes%20BJP%20to%20power%2C%20it%20will%20get%20a%20Backward%20Caste%20Chief%20Minister.%20The%20party's%20hope%20is%20to%20reel%20in%20the%20community%2C%20with%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20in%20tow.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThree%2C%20the%20BJP%20knows%20there%20is%20a%20Telugu%20Desam%20support%20base%20in%20Telangana%2C%20in%20areas%20in%20and%20around%20Hyderabad%2C%20Nalgonda%20and%20Khammam.%20Amit%20Shah%20met%20Naidu's%20son%20Nara%20Lokesh%20in%20New%20Delhi%20when%20the%20TDP%20chief%20was%20still%20inside%20Rajahmundry%20Jail.%20Lokesh%20said%20it%20was%20Telangana%20BJP%20chief%20Kishan%20Reddy%20who%20had%20contacted%20him.%20Also%20present%20at%20the%20meeting%20was%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20BJP%20chief%20Purandeswari%2C%20who%20happens%20to%20be%20Lokesh's%20maternal%20aunt%20and%20Naidu's%20sister-in-law.%20However%2C%20the%20optics%20was%20apparently%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20TDP%20supporters%20in%20Telangana.%20To%20convey%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20no%20role%20in%20sending%20Naidu%20to%20jail%20and%20that%20they%20were%20empathetic%20to%20Lokesh%20and%20Naidu's%20plight.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20appears%20to%20have%20earned%20the%20anger%20of%20those%20sympathetic%20to%20Naidu%20in%20Telangana%2C%20by%20failing%20to%20say%20and%20do%20the%20right%20things%20soon%20after%20his%20arrest.%20KCR's%20party%20did%20not%20allow%20public%20protests%20in%20Hi-Tech%20City%2C%20citing%20security%20concerns%2C%20and%20that%20is%20an%20area%20whose%20development%20is%20credited%20by%20many%20to%20Chandrababu%20Naidu.%20The%20BRS%20tried%20to%20make%20amends%2C%20with%20statements%20by%20former%20TDP%20leaders%2C%20and%20BRS%20ministers%20like%20Puvvada%20Ajay%20in%20Khammam%2C%20a%20border%20district%20where%20the%20TDP%20has%20influence.%20A%20BRS%20candidate%20from%20Serilingampally%2C%20that%20has%20a%20significant%20population%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20in%20the%20hitech%20city%20area%20of%20Hyderabad%2C%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20participate%20in%20the%2025-year%20celebrations%20of%20Hi-Tech%20city%2C%20which%20were%20aimed%20at%20celebrating%20Naidu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20attempt%20is%20to%20try%20and%20stop%20the%20%26quot%3BTDP%20supporter-Telanganite%20of%20Andhra%20Origin-Settler-turned-native-Kamma%20voter-Naidu%20empathiser%20vote%26quot%3B%20from%20going%20to%20the%20Congress%20that%20is%20now%20headed%20by%20Naidu's%20once%20close%20confidante%20Revanth%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20could%20hope%20that%20since%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20is%20now%20Naidu's%20closest%20ally%2C%20by%20extension%20that%20vote%20could%20move%20the%20BJP-Jana%20Sena%20way.%20If%20it%20doesn't%20work%2C%20the%20BJP%20could%20also%20use%20this%20to%20tell%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20that%20there%20is%20no%20point%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20TDP%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20if%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20vote%20won't%20get%20transferred%20to%20the%20Jana%20Sena.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20gets%20tickets%20far%20beyond%20his%20political%20weight%20in%20Telangana%20is%20a%20cause%20for%20resentment%20within%20the%20BJP%20among%20those%20who%20feel%20they%20should%20not%20cede%20ground%20in%20and%20around%20Hyderabad%20where%20the%20party%20has%20an%20electoral%20base.%20However%2C%20they%20have%20to%20weigh%20the%20larger%20picture.%20Interestingly%2C%20after%20a%20meeting%20with%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20BJP%20Telangana%20chief%20Kishen%20Reddy%20said%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20support%20had%20helped%20the%20BJP%20perform%20well%20in%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(GHMC)%20elections%20in%20December%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20much%20the%20BJP%20gains%20from%20partnering%20with%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20would%20not%20be%20as%20politically%20significant%20as%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20own%20party%20performance%20in%20these%20elections.%20A%20poor%20show%20would%20certainly%20provide%20cannon%20fodder%20for%20his%20rival%20Jagan%20Reddy%2C%20who%20is%20gunning%20for%20the%20showman%20politician%20at%20every%20possible%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20is%20likely%20to%20use%20the%20BJP-Jana%20Sena%20alliance%20to%20spotlight%20the%20%26quot%3BDelhi-Andhra%20hand%26quot%3B%20in%20these%20elections.%20Already%2C%20YSR%20Telangana%20Party%20leader%20YS%20Sharmila's%20unconditional%20support%20to%20the%20Congress%20is%20being%20spoken%20about%20in%20the%20same%20tone.%20KCR%2C%20who%20fought%20both%20the%202014%20and%202018%20elections%20on%20the%20Telangana%20self-respect%20card%2C%20could%20use%20the%20same%20antagonist%20narrative%20to%20keep%20the%20new%20state%20free%20of%20control%20from%20Delhi%20and%20Andhra.%20After%20all%2C%20any%20story%20gets%20the%20audience%20more%20involved%20and%20engaged%20when%20it%20has%20an%20identifiable%20%26quot%3Benemy%26quot%3B%20and%20an%20Us%20vs%20Them%20dynamic.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699353540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Ftin4s3hg_pawan-kalyan-1200-_625x300_07_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frelationship-status-of-bjp-pawan-kalyan-c-naidu-complicated-4553796%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pawan%20Kalyan%20makes%20one%20public%20appearance%20with%20PM%20Modi%20in%20Hyderabad%20and%20the%20BJP%20allots%20half%20a%20dozen%20seats%20to%20his%20Jana%20Sena%20in%20Telangana.%20This%2C%20when%20the%20actor-politician%20is%20already%20electorally%20committed%20to%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frelationship-status-of-bjp-pawan-kalyan-c-naidu-complicated-4553796%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Interview%20%7C%20Denied%20Ticket%2C%20BJP's%20Muslim%20Leader%20in%20Rajasthan%20Quits%20Party%20to%20Contest%20as%20an%20Independent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07145141%2FYunus-Khan.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20not%20fielded%20even%20a%20single%20Muslim%20in%20any%20of%20the%20200%20Assembly%20constituencies%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20where%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20on%20November%2025.%20In%20the%202018%20elections%2C%20however%2C%20the%20party%20had%20fielded%20Yunus%20Khan%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20from%20the%20Tonk%20seat%2C%20which%20he%20lost%20to%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Sachin%20Pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhan%20had%20been%20MLA%20twice%20from%20Didwana%20before%20he%20contested%20and%20lost%20from%20Tonk%20in%202018.%20His%20hopes%20of%20obtaining%20a%20BJP%20ticket%20this%20time%20around%20from%20either%20Didwana%20or%20Tonk%20have%20been%20dashed%2C%20prompting%20him%20to%20quit%20the%20party%20and%20contest%20as%20an%20Independent%20candidate%20from%20the%20Didwana%20segment.%20He%20has%20been%20a%20close%20confidant%20of%20Vasundhara%20Raje%2C%20in%20whose%20government%20he%20served%20as%20transport%20minister%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20exclusively%20to%20Khan%2C%20and%20below%20are%20the%20excerpts%20from%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%20%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20do%20you%20think%20the%20BJP%20has%20decided%20not%20to%20field%20you%20from%20either%20Didwana%20or%20Tonk%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20senior%20leadership%20not%20to%20give%20me%20a%20ticket.%20The%20party%20has%20done%20injustice%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Didwana%20by%20not%20giving%20me%20a%20ticket%2C%20as%20the%20people%20there%20wanted%20me%20to%20contest%20this%20election.%20This%20is%20the%20second%20time%20that%20the%20party%20has%20decided%20to%20ignore%20the%20wishes%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Didwana.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20have%20decided%20to%20contest%20from%20the%20constituency%20as%20an%20Independent%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDespite%20being%20known%20as%20a%20confidant%20of%20Vasundhara%20Raje%2C%20the%20party%20has%20denied%20you%20a%20ticket.%20In%20fact%2C%20several%20other%20leaders%20like%20Rajpal%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20from%20Jhotwara%20and%20Bhawani%20Singh%20Rajawat%20in%20Ladpura%20have%20been%20denied%20tickets.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20we%20three%20were%20denied%20tickets%20by%20the%20party%2C%20but%20many%20others%20who%20have%20been%20loyal%20to%20Raje%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20a%20ticket%20this%20time%3B%20Ashok%20Parnami%20is%20another%20example.%20Counting%20us%20in%20someone%E2%80%99s%20group%20is%20not%20the%20right%20thing%2C%20as%20we%20have%20been%20party%20workers%20for%20decades.%20We%20joined%20the%20BJP%20because%20we%20believed%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20a%20party%20for%20change%2C%20and%20they%20also%20wanted%20to%20bring%20change.%20They%20gave%20tickets%20to%20candidates%20who%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%202018%20and%20ignored%20loyalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20you%20not%20tried%20reaching%20out%20to%20Raje%20or%20any%20other%20leader%20in%20the%20BJP%20after%20you%20realised%20that%20you%20have%20not%20been%20given%20a%20ticket%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20from%20the%20BJP%20has%20ever%20contacted%20me%20after%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20loss%20in%202018%2C%20except%20former%20chief%20minister%20Vasundhara%20Raje.%20I%20have%20never%20demanded%20a%20ticket%20or%20anything%20from%20the%20party%20in%20the%20last%2025%20years.%20The%20party%20should%20have%20given%20tickets%20to%20winnable%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%202018%20too%2C%20we%20were%20not%20given%20the%20ticket%20from%20the%20seat%20of%20your%20choice%20(Didwana)%20and%20was%20shifted%20to%20Tonk.%20You%20were%20the%20only%20member%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20to%20have%20received%20a%20ticket%20back%20then%20among%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20candidates.%20Do%20you%20think%20your%20being%20a%20Muslim%20is%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20BJP%20denying%20you%20a%20ticket%3F%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20you%20should%20say%20that%2C%20as%20I%20have%20never%20done%20politics%20on%20religion.%20I%20have%20worked%20for%20the%20party%20for%20the%20last%2025%20years.%20It%20is%20for%20the%20media%20to%20analyse%20why%20the%20party%20has%20denied%20me%20a%20ticket%20this%20time%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20you%20not%20raised%20your%20concerns%20with%20Raje%20before%20deciding%20to%20quit%20the%20party%20and%20contest%20as%20an%20Independent%20candidate%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20have%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Didwana%2C%20because%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20we%20are%20working%20for%20them%2C%20and%20the%20people%20want%20me%20to%20contest%20the%20elections%2C%20so%20I%20am%20contesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20think%20if%20the%20BJP%20comes%20to%20power%2C%20they%20will%20make%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20the%20chief%20minister%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20comment%20on%20it%2C%20as%20I%20left%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699353051000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07145141%2FYunus-Khan.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-denied-ticket-bjps-muslim-leader-in-rajasthan-quits-party-to-contest-as-an-independent%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20transport%20minister%20and%20Vasundhara%20Raje's%20confidant%2C%20Yunus%20Khan%2C%20had%20hoped%20to%20contest%20on%20a%20BJP%20ticket%20from%20Didwana.%20However%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20not%20fielded%20even%20a%20single%20Muslim%20candidate%20from%20any%20of%20the%20200%20constituencies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-denied-ticket-bjps-muslim-leader-in-rajasthan-quit