5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHow%20McDonald's%20portrays%20the%20Egg%20McMuffin.%20%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20classic%20Egg%20McMuffin%20sandwich%20with%20a%20side%20of%20hash%20browns%20is%20my%20go-to%20meal%20whenever%20I%20travel%20and%20need%20breakfast%20on%20the%20road%20or%20at%20the%20airport.%20How%20can%20you%20resist%20the%20iconic%20sandwich%20created%20by%20a%20California%20McDonald's%20franchisee%20named%20Herb%20Peterson%20in%201971%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20his%20take%20on%20an%20eggs%20Benedict.%20But%20instead%20of%20putting%20hollandaise%20sauce%20on%20a%20fast-food%20item%2C%20Peterson%20added%20a%20slice%20of%20cheese%20and%20a%20piece%20of%20Canadian%20bacon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20always%20been%20a%20fun%20meal%2C%20and%20it%20kicked%20off%20the%20legendary%20breakfast%20service%20of%20McDonald's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20the%20Egg%20McMuffin%20didn't%20hold%20up%20to%20its%20rep.%20The%20egg%20was%20yucky%2C%20and%20the%20Canadian%20bacon%20was%20rubbery.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Egg%20McMuffin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654568c5b788914e55505d04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHere's%20what%20the%20Egg%20McMuffin%20really%20looks%20like.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Egg%20McMuffin%20requires%20McDonald's%20to%20use%20a%20proprietary%20ring%20to%20give%20the%20egg%20a%20round%20shape.%20It's%20why%20the%20Egg%20McMuffin%20was%20such%20an%20innovative%20breakfast%20offering%20when%20it%20launched%20decades%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20maybe%20it's%20better%20on%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20taste%20test%2C%20the%20egg%20tasted%20like%20powdered%20yolks.%20And%20the%20muffin%20was%20too%20spongy%20in%20texture%2C%20instead%20of%20toasty.%20The%20slice%20of%3Cstrong%3E%20%3