m.%20I%20ordered%20a%20McGriddle%20with%20bacon%2C%20cheese%2C%20and%20a%20folded%20egg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Crunchwrap%20was%20stuffed%20with%20bacon%2C%20eggs%2C%20cheese%2C%20and%20a%20hash%20brown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20syrup-soaked%20McGriddle%20is%20so%20sweet%2C%20you%20can't%20taste%20anything%20else.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221570%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20syrup%20on%20the%20McGriddle%20overpowers%20this%20sandwich%20so%20much%2C%20you%20can't%20taste%20anything%20else.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654571483cc84b4dfafc85ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221362%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20syrup%20on%20the%20McGriddle%20overpowers%20the%20sandwich.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20sandwich%20tastes%20like%20a%20handheld%20stack%20of%20pancakes%20soaked%20in%20cloyingly%20sweet%20syrup.%20I%20couldn't%20even%20taste%20the%20bacon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20wacky%2C%20innovative%20product%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20worth%20getting%20if%20you%20can't%20taste%20the%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Breakfast%20Crunchwrap%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20the%20work%20of%20a%20culinary%20genius.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taco%20Bell's%20Breakfast%20Crunchwrap%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6545778fb788914e555064bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaco%20Bell's%20Breakfast%20Crunchwrap%20is%20a%20top-notch%20innovation.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20product-innovation%20team%20at%20Taco%20Bell%20is%20top-notch.%20It%20has%20won%20the%20palates%20of%20hungry%20millennials%20for%20years%20with%20its%20Mexican-inspired%20creations.%20Every%20menu%20item%20comes%20with%20a%20Taco%20Bell%20twist%2C%20and%20that's%20what%20you%20get%20with%20the%20Breakfast%20Crunchwrap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20cross%20between%20a%20burrito%20and%20a%20quesadilla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20get%20the%20Crunchwrap%20with%20sausage%20or%20bacon.%20The%20chain%20also%20sells%20a%20Cali-inspired%20version%20with%20eggs%2C%20bacon%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20guacamole%2C%20cheddar%20cheese%2C%20and%20a%20hash%20brown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20the%20Crunchwrap%20with%20bacon.%20The%20ingenious%20part%20of%20this%20Crunchwrap%20is%20the%20presentation.%20The%20ingredients%20(choice%20of%20meat%2C%20a%20hash%20brown%2C%20scrambled%20eggs%2C%20cheese%2C%20and%20creamy%20jalape%C3%B1o%20sauce)%20are%20wrapped%20with%20a%20toasted%20hexagon-shaped%20tortilla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20bit%20of%20magic%20to%20the%20wrap%20because%20it%20doesn't%20fall%20apart%20like%20a%20burrito%20or%20taco%20with%20the%20same%20indulgent%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20perfect%20handheld%20breakfast%20meal.%20You%20can%20taste%20each%20component%20in%20every%20bite.%20The%20creamy%20jalape%C3%B1o%20sauce%20makes%20the%20wrap%20addicting.%20I%20found%20myself%20taking%20frequent%20bites%20because%20it%20brought%20so%20much%20flavor%20to%20the%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMcDonald's%20and%20Taco%20Bell%20both%20offer%20a%20sausage%20burrito%20with%20eggs.%20I%20tried%20both%20for%20a%20true%20head-to-head%20comparison.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20McDonald's%20sausage%20burrito.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6545798a3cc84b4dfafc868a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20sausage%20crumbles%20in%20the%20McDonald's%20burrito%20looked%20nasty.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20sliced%20open%20my%20McDonald's%20sausage%20burrito%20to%20look%20inside%2C%20I%20gasped.%20The%20sausage%20crumbles%20looked%20nasty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20grayish%20chunks%20looked%20like%20an%20olive