ul%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fkatephillipson%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EKate%20Phillipson%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20her%20family%20she%20was%20moving%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-life-in-bahrain-2013-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBahrain%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20were%20shocked%2C%20as%20it's%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fforeign-travel-advice%2Fbahrain%2Flocal-laws-and-customs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econservative%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%20whose%20state%20religion%20is%20Islam%20and%20near%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-fighting-war-3-fronts-hamas-lebanon-syria-middle-east-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewar-torn%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Middle%20East.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20perception%20they%20had%2C%20that%20I%20had%2C%20about%20the%20area%3F%20It%20couldn't%20be%20farther%20from%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20Phillipson%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2031-year-old%20Briton%20arrived%20in%202020%20with%20her%20then-boyfriend%2C%20a%20navy%20sailor%2C%20after%20he%20was%20transferred%20there%2C%20and%20she%20chose%20to%20follow%20him.%20Now%20single%2C%20she%20works%20in%20the%20luxury-interior-design%20business%20as%20a%20marketing%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhillipson%20is%20part%20of%20a%20group%20of%20expats%20who've%20moved%20to%20this%20tiny%20nation%2C%20which%20sits%2016%20miles%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20Many%20are%20lured%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.travelguide-en.org%2Fbahrain-climate%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520very%2520few%2520rains%252C%2520Bahrain%2Cdays%2520of%2520rain%2520per%2520month.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethe%20sunshine%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20lifestyle%20similar%20to%20Dubai's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhillipson%20describes%20life%20in%20Bahrain%20as%20idyll%20%E2%80%94%20as%20it%20is%20for%20many%20educated%2C%20mostly%20Western%20professionals%20who%20have%20arrived%20in%20Bahrain%20like%20her.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnews%2Fworldviews%2Fwp%2F2015%2F02%2F25%2Fwatch-a-bahraini-tries-living-a-day-in-the-life-of-a-migrant-worker%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20life%20of%20more%20than%20half%20of%20her%20fellow%20residents%20is%20very%20different%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20that's%20the%20number%20estimated%20to%20be%20migrant%20workers%20from%20South%20Asia%20who%20hold%20jobs%20in%20the%20construction%20and%20service%20industries%20on%20low%20wages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20legally%20mandated%20minimum%20wage%20for%20non-nationals%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.migrant-rights.org%2F2022%2F07%2Fwhile-private-sector-profits-soar-migrants-in-bahrain-struggle-with-low-wages-and-rising-living-costs%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBahrain%2520has%2520no%2520minimum%2520wage%2CUS%2524%2520530)%2520a%2520month.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eone%20estimate%20indicated%20that%20more%20than%2070%25%20of%20those%20working%20in%20the%20private%20sector%20there%20earn%20less%20than%20%24530%20per%20month%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Many%20arrive%20under%20private%20sponsorship%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cfr.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Fwhat-kafala-system%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20system%20known%20in%20the%20region%20as%20%26quot%3Bkafala%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20which%20creates%20greater%20potential%20for%20abuse%2C%20an%20issue%20that's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrw.org%2Fnews%2F2012%2F09%2F30%2Fbahrain-abuse-migrant-workers-despite-reforms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ean%20ongoing%20area%20of%20concern%20for%20non%20profits%20like%20Human%20Rights%20Watch.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWork%20is%20very%20different%20in%20Bahrain%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20how%20to%20find%20a%20job%20but%20also%20when%20you're%20on%20the%20clock%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPhillipson%20said%20moving%20for%20her%20wasn't%20difficult%20%E2%80%94%20UK%20citizens%2C%20as%20well%20as%20US%20passport%20holders%2C%20can%20obtain%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.state.gov%2Fcontent%2Ftravel%2Fen%2Finternational-travel%2FInternational-Travel-Country-Information-Pages%2FBahrain.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Evisa%20on%20arrival%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20worked%20in%20marketing%20in%20London%20and%20assumed%20it%20would%20be%20easy%20to%20segue%20into%20a%20similar%20position.%20But%20she%20applied%20for%20several%20roles%20without%20success%2C%20so%20instead%2C%20she%20took%20a%20job%20as%20a%20VIP%20hostess%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsolymarbahrain.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESolymar%20Beach%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20St.%20Tropez-inspired%20beach%20club.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20through%20a%20customer%20there%20that%20she%20networked%20her%20way%20in%20May%20into%20her%20current%20role%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lightex.com.bh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELightex%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20acts%20as%20an%20intermediary%20between%20high-end%20interiors%20firms%20in%20France%2C%20Italy%2C%20and%20the%20like%20and%20the%20local%20Bahraini%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20culture%20difference%20because%20I%20come%20from%20the%20world%20of%20grad%20schemes%20and%20formal%20processes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20here%2C%20it's%20very%20much%20who%20you%20know%2C%20not%20what%20you%20know.%20So%20many%20of%20my%20friends%20have%20ended%20up%20in%20these%20amazing%20jobs%20that%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20much-stronger%20work-life%20balance%2C%20she%20said%2C%20with%20less%20expectation%20to%20be%20on%20call%20outside%20office%20hours%20compared%20with%20her%20London%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20workweek%20runs%20Sunday%20through%20Thursday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenationalnews.com%2Fmena%2F2021%2F12%2F07%2Fwhen-is-the-weekend-in-the-arab-world%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eas%20is%20typical%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20be%20back%20at%20work%2C%20and%20my%20friends%20in%20England%20are%20having%20roast%20dinners%2C%20messaging%20me%20about%20what%20they're%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20you%20get%20adjusted%20to%20it%2C%20and%20if%20we%20have%20a%20big%20project%20with%20a%20big%20deadline%2C%20we%20might%20take%20the%20odd%20work%20call%20from%20Europe%20on%20a%20Friday.%20You%20have%20to%20be%20fairly%20flexible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20are%202%20major%20upsides%20to%20living%20there%3A%20safety%20and%20sunshine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20woman%20next%20to%20a%20camel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65257e9d6561dd877e762c2d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPhillipson%20in%20Bahrain.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kate%20Phillipson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPhillipson%20said%20the%20rest%20of%20her%20life%20is%20a%20marked%20improvement%20on%20her%20day-to-day%20in%20dreary%20London%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20see%20sunshine%20pretty%20much%20every%20single%20day%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20know%20anywhere%20in%20the%20UK%20that%20would%20be%20possible%20%E2%80%94%20it%20makes%20such%20a%20difference%20in%20your%20mood%20and%20energy%20levels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20misses%20little%20about%20her%20former%20home%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20direct%20six-hour%20flight%20to%20see%20her%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20mum%20came%20to%20visit%20last%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe%20loved%20it%2C%20and%20she%20said%2C%20'I%20understand%20why%20you%20love%20it%20here%20now.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20Bahrain%20is%20easier%20for%20a%20young%20woman%20than%20anywhere%20she'd%20been%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20never%20felt%20safer%20in%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20worked%20in%20hospitality%2C%20I%20might%20finish%20at%201%3A30%20or%202%3A00%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20and%20I'd%20walk%20back%20to%20my%20apartment%20and%20go%20for%20a%20run%20at%203%3A00%20a.m.%20if%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20sleep%20yet.%20There's%20not%20really%20anywhere%20in%20the%20UK%20I%20would%20feel%20comfortable%20doing%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhillipson%20said%20she%20regularly%20leaves%20her%20purse%20and%20keys%20on%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20table%20when%20going%20inside%20to%20order%20or%20chat%20with%20the%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20never%20in%20my%20wildest%20dreams%20worry%20about%20someone%20taking%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldnomads.com%2Ftravel-safety%2Fmiddle-east%2Fbahrain%2Flaws-and-customs-in-bahrain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epunishments%20for%20crime%20are%20so%20severe%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20the%20weekend%2C%20Bahrain%20becomes%20the%20Middle%20East's%20answer%20to%20Las%20Vegas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20restrictive%20dress%20code%20for%20women%20is%20another%20Middle%20Eastern%20tradition%20that's%20much%20less%20widespread%20in%20Bahrain%20than%20in%20many%20adjoining%2C%20majority-Muslim%20countries%2C%20Phillipson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20aware%20that%20I%20have%20to%20be%20a%20little%20more%20conservatively%20dressed%20than%20in%20London%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20Bahrain%20is%20very%20liberal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20a%20hot%20spot%20for%20many%20young%20Saudis%20each%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20a%20young%20Saudi%20guy%20saying%20to%20me%2C%20'This%20is%20our%20Las%20Vegas%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20come%20every%20weekend%20if%20they%20have%20the%20money.%20They%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20drink%2C%20have%20nice%20dinners%2C%20and%20dress%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20Westernized.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20country's%20attitude%20toward%20alcohol%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fforeign-travel-advice%2Fbahrain%2Flocal-laws-and-customs%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAlcohol%2Cwithdrawal%2520of%2520their%2520driving%2520licence.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eis%20markedly%20more%20relaxed%20than%20that%20of%20many%20nearby%20Gulf%20states%20with%20similar%20demographics%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Alcohol%20is%20not%20sold%20in%20supermarkets%20and%20malls%2C%20Phillipson%20said%2C%20but%20there%20are%20designated%20stores%20where%20you%20can%20buy%20it%20to%20take%20home%20and%20drink%20at%20your%20house%2C%20and%20restaurants%20and%20bars%20sell%20alcohol%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisiting%20rooftop%20bars%20is%20a%20big%20part%20of%20Phillipson's%20life.%20She%20said%20that%20she's%20found%20the%20international%20residents%20in%20Bahrain%20very%20welcoming%20and%20has%20easily%20made%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20in%20her%20close%20circle%2C%20she%20counts%20Turkish%2C%20Saudi%2C%20Azeri%2C%20and%20Ethiopian%20incomers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20fellow%20Britons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPhillipson%20plans%20to%20stay%20long%20term%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPhillipson%20said%20her%20salary%20is%20lower%20than%20it%20would%20be%20in%20a%20comparable%20role%20in%20Europe%2C%20but%20she%20has%20more%20spending%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20disposable%20income%20is%20a%20lot%20higher%2C%20so%20I%20feel%20better%20off%20even%20though%20I'm%20earning%20less%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20two-bedroom%20luxury%20apartment%20like%20hers%20typically%20cost%20between%20%24900%20and%20%241%2C000%20in%20rent%20a%20month.%20The%20average%20rent%20in%20London%2C%20in%20comparison%2C%20sits%20at%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-london-66393257%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%C2%A32%2C700%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20about%20%243%2C300.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pace%20of%20life%20is%20slower%20and%20more%20comfortable%20out%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'd%20not%20even%20heard%20of%20it%20before%20I%20moved%20here%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20plans%20on%20leaving%20anytime%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-london-bahrain-british-milennial-shares-what-its-like-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699352341000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65257eb368f1d46f52ad4c84%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-london-bahrain-british-milennial-shares-what-its-like-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kate%20Phillipson%20moved%20from%20the%20UK%20to%20Bahrain%20in%202020.%20She%20switched%20careers%20and%20now%20enjoys%20more%20sunshine%2C%20a%20lower%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20and%20a%20safer%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Mark%20Ellwood)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-london-bahrain-british-milennial-shares-what-its-like-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Salman%20got%20injured%20on%20the%20sets%20of%20Tiger%203%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699352301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105038368%2Cimgsize-71518.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhen-salman-khan-injured-hims