k.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flate-stage-startups-vc-lack-funding-forced-shut-down-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVC%3C%2Fa%3E%20firm%20said%20AI%20investments%20are%20so%20huge%20that%20any%20new%20rules%20around%20the%20content%20used%20to%20train%20models%20%26quot%3Bwill%20significantly%20disrupt%26quot%3B%20the%20investment%20community's%20plans%20and%20expectations%20around%20the%20technology%2C%20according%20to%20comments%20submitted%20to%20the%20US%20Copyright%20Office.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bottom%20line%20is%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%2C%20known%20as%20a16z%2C%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BImposing%20the%20cost%20of%20actual%20or%20potential%20copyright%20liability%20on%20the%20creators%20of%20AI%20models%20will%20either%20kill%20or%20significantly%20hamper%20their%20development.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20USCO%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-copyright-office-new-rules-generative-ai-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsidering%20new%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20AI%20that%20specifically%20address%20the%20tech%20industry's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-copyright-meta-google-openai-a16z-microsoft%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efree%20use%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20owned%20and%20copyrighted%20content%20to%20train%20large%20language%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA16z%20argued%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bonly%20practical%20way%26quot%3B%20LLMs%20can%20be%20trained%20is%20via%20huge%20amounts%20of%20copyrighted%20content%20and%20data%2C%20including%2C%20%26quot%3Bsomething%20approaching%20the%20entire%20corpus%20of%20the%20written%20word%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Ban%20enormous%20cross-section%20of%20all%20of%20the%20publicly%20available%20information%20ever%20published%20on%20the%20internet.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20VC%20firm%20has%20invested%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fa16z.com%2Fai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Escores%20of%20AI%20companies%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20startups%20based%20on%20its%20%26quot%3Bexpectation%26quot%3B%20that%20all%20this%20copyrighted%20content%20was%20and%20will%20remain%20available%20as%20training%20data%20through%20%26quot%3Bfair%20use%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20no%20payment%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENational%20security%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20expectations%20have%20been%20a%20critical%20factor%20in%20the%20enormous%20investment%20of%20private%20capital%20into%20US-based%20AI%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20a16z%20said.%20%26quot%3BUndermining%20those%20expectations%20will%20jeopardize%20future%20investment%2C%20along%20with%20U.S.%20economic%20competitiveness%20and%20national%20security.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20praised%20the%20current%20US%20copyright%20system%20for%20striking%20the%20right%20balance%20between%20%26quot%3Bprotection%20expression%26quot%3B%20and%20supporting%20%26quot%3Bnon-exploitive%26quot%3B%20uses%20of%20copyrighted%20material.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20the%20same%20token%2C%20the%20best%20way%20to%20lose%20the%20United%20States'%20current%20leadership%20in%20the%20burgeoning%20AI%20industry%E2%80%94along%20with%20economic%20competitiveness%20and%20national%20security%20benefits%20that%20leadership%20brings%E2%80%94is%20by%20rushing%20to%20pass%20legislation%20that%20undermines%20the%20long-standing%20and%20principled%20approach%20to%20copyright%20law%20that%20has%20made%20this%20country%20both%20a%20creative%20and%20technological%20leader%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20wrote.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20spending%20time%20on%20making%20new%20laws%20that%20would%20explicitly%20address%20AI%2C%20the%20VC%20firm%20said%20the%20USCO%20should%20%26quot%3Bembrace%20it%20wholeheartedly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20afford%20to%20be%20outpaced%20in%20areas%20like%20cybersecurity%2C%20intelligence%20operations%2C%20a