d%20concern%20over%20the%20use%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20to%20spread%20disinformation%2C%20according%20to%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20has%20issued%20an%20advisory%20to%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20underlining%20the%20legal%20provisions%20that%20cover%20such%20deepfakes%20and%20the%20penalties%20their%20creation%20and%20circulation%20may%20attract.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20cited%20Section%2066D%20of%20Information%20Technoloy%20Act%2C%202000.%20The%20section%2C%20which%20relates%20to%20'punishment%20for%20cheating%20by%20personation%20by%20using%20computer%20resource'%2C%20states%2C%20%26quot%3BWhoever%2C%20by%20means%20for%20any%20communication%20device%20or%20computer%20resource%20cheats%20by%20personating%2C%20shall%20be%20punished%20with%20imprisonment%20of%20either%20description%20for%20a%20term%20which%20may%20extend%20to%20three%20years%20and%20shall%20also%20be%20liable%20to%20fine%20which%20may%20extend%20to%20one%20lakh%20rupees.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%20advisory%20comes%20amid%20shock%20and%20concern%20over%20a%20viral%20video%20that%20appeared%20to%20show%20Ms%20Mandanna%20entering%20an%20elevator.%20Soon%20after%20the%20clip%20started%20trending%2C%20it%20was%20found%20that%20it%20was%20actually%20a%20video%20of%20British-Indian%20influencer%20Zara%20Patel.%20The%20visuals%20were%20doctored%20using%20deepfake%20technology%20and%20the%20result%20was%20jaw-dropping%20-%20Ms%20Patel's%20face%20was%20replaced%20with%20that%20of%20Ms%20Mandanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20revelation%20sparked%20concerns%20over%20the%20ramification%20of%20such%20tinkering%2C%20especially%20for%20public%20figures%2C%20who%20may%20get%20in%20trouble%20over%20visuals%20their%20faces%20are%20doctored%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Mandanna%20said%20this%20episode%20is%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20scary%26quot%3B.%20''I%20feel%20really%20hurt%20to%20share%20this%20and%20have%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20deepfake%20video%20of%20me%20being%20spread%20online.%20Something%20like%20this%20is%20honestly%2C%20extremely%20scary%20not%20only%20for%20me%2C%20but%20also%20for%20each%20one%20of%20us%20who%20today%20is%20vulnerable%20to%20so%20much%20harm%20because%20of%20how%20technology%20is%20being%20misused%2C''%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20voices%20in%20the%20film%20industry%2C%20including%20legendary%20actor%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20flagged%20the%20matter%20and%20called%20for%20legal%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajeev%20Chandrsekhar%2C%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%2C%20yesterday%20said%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20safety%20and%20trust%20for%20Indins.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20IT%20rules%20notified%20in%20April%2C%202023%20-%20it%20is%20a%20legal%20obligation%20for%20platforms%20to%20ensure%20no%20misinformation%20is%20posted%20by%20any%20user%2C%20ensure%20that%20when%20reported%20by%20any%20user%20or%20govt%2C%20misinformation%20is%20removed%20in%2036%20hrs.%20If%20platforms%20do%20not%20comply%20wth%20this%2C%20rule%207%20will%20apply%20and%20platforms%20can%20be%20taken%20to%20court%20by%20aggrieved%20person%20under%20provisions%20of%20IPC.%20Deep%20fakes%20are%20latest%20and%20even%20more%20dangerous%20and%20damaging%20form%20of%20misinformation%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20dealt%20with%20by%20platforms%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20tweeted%20yesterday%20with%20the%20hashtags%20%26quot%3BSafeTrustedInternet%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BAccountable%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BDigitalIndia%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20video%2C%20however%2C%20can%20still%20be%20seen%20on%20social%20media%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699349520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fuqln4gbg_rashmika-mandanna_625x300_06_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.