C%20No%20Job%20for%20Protesting%20Actresses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07144013%2Fimage.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20late%20October%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Culture%20and%20Islamic%20Guidance%20in%20Iran%20published%20a%20list%20of%20actresses%20barred%20from%20their%20profession%20for%20appearing%20in%20public%20without%20a%20headscarf.%20Culture%20and%20Islamic%20Guidance%20minister%20Mohammad%20Mehdi%20Esmaili%20said%20it%20was%20not%20possible%20to%20work%20with%20those%20who%20did%20not%20observe%20the%20mandatory%20hijab%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20list%20contains%20some%2020%20names%2C%20including%20world-famous%20artists%20like%20Taraneh%20Alidoosti.%20Now%2039%2C%20she%20starred%20in%20the%20internationally%20acclaimed%20drama%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fthe-salesman%2Fa-37187587%5C%22%3EThe%20Salesman%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202016.%20The%20film%20won%20director%20Asghar%20Farhadi%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fthe-oscars%2Ft-17455571%5C%22%3EOscar%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20Best%20Foreign%20Language%20Film%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EActress%20arrested%20for%20social%20media%20post%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlidoosti%20used%20to%20wear%20a%20headscarf%20in%20public%20even%20when%20she%20was%20abroad.%20But%20that%20changed%20in%20November%202022%20as%20Iran%20was%20rocked%20by%C2%A0protests%20following%20the%20death%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fjina-mahsa-amini%2Ft-63431146%5C%22%3EJina%20Mahsa%20Amini%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%2022-year-old%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Firans-morality-police-resume-headscarf-patrols-in-cities%2Fa-66247907%5C%22%3Eso-called%20morality%20police%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20violating%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20Islamic%20dress%20code%20and%20died%20later%20in%20police%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Instagram%2C%20Alidoosti%20posted%20a%20picture%20of%20herself%20without%20a%20headscarf.%20Her%20account%C2%A0has%20over%208%20million%20followers.%20The%20image%20shows%20her%20holding%20a%20slip%20of%20paper%20that%20reads%20%E2%80%9Cwomen%2C%20life%2C%20freedom%E2%80%9D%20to%20show%20support%20for%20the%20Iranian%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20movement%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Firan-protests%2Ft-63439309%5C%22%3Eanti-government%20protests%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20posting%20the%20image%2C%20Alidoosti%20was%20arrested%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Firan-releases-film-star-jailed-for-backing-protests%2Fa-64285839%5C%22%3Eonly%20released%20two%20weeks%20later%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0after%20friends%20and%20family%20posted%20bail.%20On%20social%20media%2C%20she%20responded%20to%20her%20employment%20ban%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20not%20comply%20with%20your%20headscarf%20that%20is%20still%20dripping%20with%20the%20blood%20of%20my%20sisters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFailure%20to%20cover%20one%E2%80%99s%20head%20in%20public%20can%20be%20deadly%20for%20women%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Firan%2Ft-18996175%5C%22%3EIran%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0as%20the%20recent%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Firan-teen-armita-geravand-brain-dead-after-hijab-incident%2Fa-67177851%5C%22%3Edeath%20of%2017-year-old%20Armita%20Geravand%3C%2Fa%3E%20unfortunately%20proves.%20In%20early%20October%2C%20the%20teenager%20was%20on%20her%20way%20to%20school%20without%20a%20headscarf.%20After%20an%20alleged%20assault%20by%20the%20so-called%20morality%20police%20on%20the%20Tehran%20metro%2C%20the%20teenager%20fell%20unconscious%20and%20was%20hospitalized%20with%20severe%20head%20trauma.%20There%20she%20remained%20in%20a%20coma%20until%20she%20was%20declared%20brain%20dead.%20She%20was%20buried%20on%20October%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYoung%20Iranian%20women%20outraged%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20Iranian%20student%20from%20the%20capital%20Tehran%20told%20DW%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20risk%20our%20lives%20every%20day%20because%20we%20are%20outside%20without%20our%20headscarves.%20It%20is%20sad%20to%20see%20that%20many%20actresses%20still%20wear%20one.%E2%80%9D%20She%20pointed%20to%20the%20recent%20gathering%20of%20film%20industry%20insiders%20at%20the%20funeral%20of%20murdered%20Iranian%20director%20Dariush%20Mehrjui%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20screenwriter%20Vahideh%20Mohammadifar%2C%20on%20October%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20mid-October%2C%20both%20had%20been%20found%20dead%20in%20their%20home%20with%20knife%20wounds.%20The%20movie%20industry%20and%20the%20wider%20public%20were%20shocked%20to%20learn%20of%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20murder.%20Authorities%20spoke%20of%20a%20robbery%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20former%20gardener.%20But%20many%20remained%20skeptical.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20other%20filmmakers%20in%20Iran%2C%20Mehrjui%20was%20often%20at%20loggerheads%20with%20state%20authorities.%20In%20March%202022%2C%20when%20his%20last%20film%20%E2%80%9CLa%20Minor%E2%80%9D%20was%20censored%2C%20the%2083-year-old%20posted%20an%20angry%20message%20to%20the%20Iran%20culture%20ministry%20on%20social%20media%2C%20stating%3A%20%E2%80%9CKill%20me%2C%20do%20whatever%20you%20want%20with%20me%20%E2%80%A6%20destroy%20me%2C%20but%20I%20want%20my%20rights.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20burial%2C%20many%20noteworthy%20actresses%20wore%20headscarves.%20The%20only%20woman%20to%20defy%20the%20obligatory%20hijab%20mandate%20was%2016-year-old%20Mona%20Mehrjui%2C%20the%20murdered%20couple%E2%80%99s%20daughter%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98The%20price%20of%20resistance%20is%20high%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20understand%20that%20the%20younger%20generation%20is%20angry%20with%20us.%20My%20generation%20is%20conservative%20and%20cautious%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0Shole%20Pakravan%20told%20DW.%20The%20stage%20actress%20and%20author%20has%20been%20living%20in%20Germany%20since%202017.%20Three%20years%20prior%2C%20her%20daughter%20Reyhaneh%20Jabbari%20was%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Firan-executes-reyhaneh-jabbari-despite-international-opposition%2Fa-18020700%5C%22%3Eexecuted%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20Iran%20for%20killing%20the%20man%20who%20tried%20to%20rape%20her.%20Pakravan%20fought%20long%20and%20hard%20to%20save%20her%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20life%C2%A0but%20was%20unsuccessful.%20Now%C2%A0she%20raises%20her%20voice%20for%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20know%20that%20right%20now%C2%A0the%20price%20of%20resistance%20in%20Iran%20is%20very%20high%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20vanish%20out%20of%20sight%2C%20you%20must%20reluctantly%20wear%20a%20headscarf.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20she%20did%20not%20believe%20that%20resistance%20in%20Iran%20had%20ended%20though.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20changed%20and%20will%20reappear%20in%20new%20forms.%20Those%20in%20power%20can%20never%20undo%20what%20happened%20last%20year%20in%20Iran.%20They%20are%20now%20facing%20a%20young%20and%20courageous%20generation%20of%20women%20who%20know%20what%20they%20want%3A%20Freedom%20and%20the%20end%20of%20oppression.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%20data-preserver-spaces%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Firan-no-headscarf-no-job-for-protesting-actresses%2Fa-67322600%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-stories%2Fs-9097%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20translated%20from%20German.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699348876000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07144013%2Fimage.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Firan-no-headscarf-no-job-for-protesting-actresses%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Iranian%20actresses%20who%20defy%20Iran's%20so-called%20morality%20police%20and%20go%20out%20in%20the%20public%20without%20a%20headscarf%20have%20been%20banned%20from%20working.%20Many%20remain%20defiant%20even%20as%20locals%20pay%20an%20increasingly%20high%20price%20for%20protest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Firan-no-headscarf-no-job-for-protesting-actresses%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Allahabad%20And%20Faizabad%2C%20Aligarh%20In%20Line%20For%20A%20Name%20Change%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20Allahabad%2C%20another%20prominent%20city%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20may%20be%20staring%20at%20a%20name%20change.%20The%20Aligarh%20Municipal%20Corporation%20has%20unanimously%20passed%20a%20proposal%20to%20change%20the%20city's%20name%20to%20Harigarh.%20The%20proposal%20was%20presented%20by%20Mayor%20Prashant%20Singhal%20in%20a%20meeting%20yesterday%20and%20was%20supported%20by%20all%20councillors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20greenlights%20the%20proposal%20to%20rename%20Aligarh%2C%20it%20will%20add%20to%20the%20growing%20tally%20of%20places%20renamed%20in%20the%20BJP-ruled%20state.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20high-profile%20recent%20examples%20is%20the%20renaming%20of%20Allahabad%20to%20Prayagraj%20in%20January%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20meeting%20yesterday%2C%20a%20proposal%20was%20presented%20to%20change%20the%20name%20of%20Aligarh%20to%20Harigarh.%20All%20councillors%20unanimously%20supported%20this.%20Now%2C%20this%20proposal%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20administration.%20I%20hope%20that%20the%20administration%20will%20take%20cognizance%20of%20this%20and%20fulfill%20our%20demand%20to%20change%20the%20name%20of%20Aligarh%20to%20Harigarh...This%20demand%20has%20been%20being%20raised%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Aligarh%20mayor%20Prashant%20Singhal%20said%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20state%20government%20can%20change%20the%20name%20of%20any%20city%20or%20area%20within%20the%20state.%20After%20a%20municipal%20body%20unanimously%20approves%20a%20proposed%20name%20change%20resolution%2C%20it%20will%20write%20to%20the%20state%20government.%20The%20resolution%20will%20then%20be%20sent%20by%20the%20state%20government%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20for%20approval.%20If%20the%20ministry%20and%20other%20relevant%20agencies%20approve%20the%20resolution%2C%20the%20state%20government%20can%20officially%20change%20the%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20proposal%20to%20rename%20Aligarh%20to%20Harigarh%20was%20cleared%20by%20a%20zila%20panchayat%20meeting%20in%202021%20and%20sent%20to%20UP%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath.%20In%202019%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Adityanath%20indicated%20that%20his%20government%20will%20keep%20up%20with%20its%20spree%20of%20renaming%20places%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20did%20what%20we%20felt%20was%20good.%20We%20renamed%20Mughal%20Sarai%20as%20Pandit%20Deen%20Dayal%20Upadhayay%20Nagar%2C%20Allahabad%20as%20Prayagraj%20and%20Faizabad%20district%20as%20Ayodhya%20district.%20Where%20there%20is%20a%20need%2C%20the%20government%20will%20take%20the%20steps%20required%2C%26quot%3B%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20name%20changes%20of%20Faizabad%20district%20and%20Allahabad%2C%20members%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20have%2C%20over%20the%20years%2C%20demanded%20that%20other%20cities%20be%20renamed%20as%20well.%20An%20Agra%20lawmaker%20had%20proposed%20that%20Agra%20be%20renamed%20Agravan%20or%20Agarwal%2C%20while%20another%20suggested%20that%20Muzaffarnagar%20be%20renamed%20Laxmi%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20coming%20to%20power%20in%20March%202017%2C%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government%20has%20renamed%20many%20projects%20and%20schemes%2C%20including%20the%20Purvanchal%20Expressway%2C%20which%20was%20initiated%20by%20the%20Akhilesh%20Yadav-led%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20SP%20government%20named%20the%20ambulance%20service%20the%20Samajwadi%20Ambulance%20Swasthya%20Sewa.%20The%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government%20renamed%20the%20service%2C%20removing%20the%20prefix%20%26quot%3BSamajwadi%26quot%3B%20and%20replacing%20it%20with%20%26quot%3BMukhya%20Mantri%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20government's%20pension%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699348800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-08%2F1eda07po_aligarh_640x480_18_August_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-allahabad-and-faizabad-aligarh-in-line-for-a-name-change-4553466%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Aligarh%20Municipal%20Corporation%20has%20unanimously%20passed%20a%20proposal%20to%20change%20the%20city's%20name%20to%20Harigarh.%20The%20proposal%20was%20presented%20by%20Mayor%20Prashant%20Singhal%20in%20a%20meeting%20yesterday%20and%20was%20supported%20by%20all%20councillors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-allahabad-and-faizabad-aligarh-in-line-for-a-name-change-4553466%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-allahabad-and-faizabad-aligarh-in-line-for-a-name-change-4553466%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-allahabad-and-faizabad-aligarh-in-line-for-a-name-change-4553466%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'34.1%25%20of%20Bihar%20households%20earning%20less%20than%20Rs%206k%2Fmonth'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699348590000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105036173%2Cimgsize-35454.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2F34-1-of