%2F09%2F02102630%2F1156px-Supreme_Court_of_India_01.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20batch%20of%20petitions%20concerning%20the%20Adani-Hindenburg%20matter%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20listed.%20It%20has%20been%20over%20two%20months%20since%20the%20matter%20was%20scheduled%20to%20be%20heard%20on%20August%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fadani-hindenburg-case-petitioners-raise-concerns-about-delay-in-listing-cji-agrees-to-look-into-the-issue-241777%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20advocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20appearing%20for%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20the%20repeated%20deferrals%20in%20listing%20the%20case%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20matter%20was%20to%20be%20listed%20on%20August%2028%2C%20but%20it%20has%20been%20deferred%2C%20deferred%2C%20deferred%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhushan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20will%20ask%20the%20registry%20to%20look%20into%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBackstory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2024%2C%20US-based%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%20published%20a%20report%20accusing%20the%20Adani%20Group%20of%20financial%20fraud%20and%20accounting%20malpractices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fanalysing-the-adani-debacle%5C%22%3Ehas%20denied%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20appointed%20an%20expert%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20regulatory%20failure%2C%20especially%20of%20SEBI%2C%20the%20stock%20market%20regulator.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20SEBI%20is%20also%20carrying%20out%20its%20own%20investigation.%20It%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fcompanies%2Fadani-hindenburg-probe-sebi-seeks-15-day-extension-to-complete-investigations%2Farticle67193501.ece%5C%22%3Ewas%20expected%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20submit%20its%20report%20to%20the%20panel%20on%20August%2014%2C%20but%20had%20been%20given%20more%20time%20to%20complete%20its%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESEBI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenergy.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Frenewable%2Fsebi-submits-status-report-on-adani-hindenburg-probe-says-awaiting-info-from-tax-havens%2F103078360%5C%22%3Esubmitted%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20status%20report%20on%20August%2025.%20But%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20hearing%20on%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20status%20report%20has%20been%20deferred.%20The%20status%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbfsi.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findustry%2Fhindenburg-adani-matter-petitioner-seeks-early-supreme-court-hearing%2F105005543%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2022%20out%20of%2024%20investigations%20are%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court-led%20expert%20committee%20has%20submitted%20its%20report%20on%20the%20matter.%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20the%20expert%20panel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fmarkets%2Fsc-appointed-panel-on-adani-group-finds-no-regulatory-failure-on-price-manipulation-report%2Farticle66869523.ece%5C%22%3Econcluded%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20would%20be%20difficult%20to%20point%20to%20a%20regulatory%20failure%20on%20the%20part%20of%20SEBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20raised%20concerns%20on%20the%20allegation%20of%20violation%20of%20minimum%20public%20shareholding.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMinimum%20public%20shareholding%20or%20free%20float%20refers%20to%20the%20shares%20of%20a%20company%20that%20can%20be%20publicly%20traded%20and%20are%20not%20restricted%20(i.e.%2C%20held%20by%20insiders).%20According%20to%20SEBI%20rules%2C%20listed%20companies%20are%20required%20to%20maintain%20a%20minimum%20public%20holding%20(or%20free%20float)%20of%2025%25.%20This%20allows%20a%20company%20to%20raise%20money%20from%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFulfilling%20this%20criteria%20is%20required%20to%20stay%20listed%20on%20the%20exchanges.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20expert%20committee%20report%20expressed%20concerns%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbecause-of-repealed-provisions-sebi-hit-opaque-structure-wall-while-investigating-adani-sc-panel%5C%22%3ESEBI%E2%80%99s%20inability%20to%20get%20adequate%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20offshore%20funds%20because%20of%20repealed%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20offshore%20funds%2C%20whose%20ultimate%20beneficiary%20is%20unknown%2C%20because%20of%20the%20countries%E2%80%99%20tax%20haven%20status%2C%20have%20immensely%20contributed%20to%20the%20growth%20of%20Adani%20Group%20companies.%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20columnist%20Andy%20Mukherjee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fcompanies%2Fgautam-adani-and-his-fortune-drivers-deserve-keener-spotlight-scrutiny-122092300102_1.html%5C%22%3Ehad%20in%20September%202022%20written%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20these%20%E2%80%9Csilent%20soldiers%E2%80%9D%2C%20or%20%E2%80%9CAdani%E2%80%99s%20fortune%20drivers%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20deserve%20some%20scrutiny%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20panel%20report%20said%20that%20these%20provisions%20of%20requiring%20FPIs%20to%20disclose%20%E2%80%9Cultimate%20natural%20person%E2%80%9D%20were%20done%20away%20with%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%202018%2C%20the%20provision%20of%20dealing%20with%20an%20%E2%80%98opaque%20structure%E2%80%99%20and%20requiring%20an%20FPI%20to%20disclose%20every%20ultimate%20natural%20person%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20chain%20of%20every%20owner%20of%20economic%20interest%20with%20the%20FPI%20was%20done%20away%20with.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20markets%20regulator%20had%20even%20approached%20the%20Organized%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%20for%20%E2%80%9Ckey%20documents%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fmarkets%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Fadani-hindenburg-case-sebi-asks-occrp-for-documents%2Farticleshow%2F104510536.cms%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20documents%20showed%20that%20SEBI%20was%20warned%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20in%202014%20about%20alleged%20stock%20manipulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20January%202014%20DRI%20alert%20was%20sent%20to%20former%20SEBI%20chairman%20U.K.%20Sinha%20that%20the%20Adani%20Group%20was%20allegedly%20siphoning%20money%20by%20overvaluing%20power%20equipment%20imports%20and%20investing%20them%20in%20listed%20companies%20via%20entities%20located%20in%20Mauritius%20and%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20network%20of%20investigative%20reporters%2C%20however%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fsebi-occrp-documents-adani-allegations%5C%22%3Erefused%3C%2Fa%3E%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20request%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20sources%20of%20information%20are%20accessible%20through%20official%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOCCRP%20told%20SEBI%20that%20its%20long-standing%20policy%20is%20not%20to%20provide%20any%20documents%20beyond%20what%20is%20published.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699348203000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02102630%2F1156px-Supreme_Court_of_India_01.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcji-chandrachud-says-hell-look-into-the-repeated-deferrals-in-sc-listing-of-adani-hindenburg-case%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20matter%20was%20to%20be%20listed%20on%20August%2028%2C%20but%20it%20has%20been%20deferred%2C%20deferred%2C%20deferred%2C'%20advocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20appearing%20for%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcji-chandrachud-says-hell-look-into-the-repeated-deferrals-in-sc-listing-of-adani-hindenburg-case%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'The%20Crown'%20Actor%20Opens%20Up%20About%20%26quot%3BDifficult%26quot%3B%20Princess%20Diana%20Scenes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EElizabeth%20Debicki%2C%20who%20is%20portraying%20the%20roles%20of%20Princess%20Diana%20in%20Netflix's%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Crown%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20has%20described%20how%20she%20felt%20shooting%20the%20tragic%20events%20on%201997.%20Speaking%20to%20reporters%20ahead%20of%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20sixth%20season%20of%20the%20royal%20drama%2C%20the%2033-year-old%20said%20the%20scenes%20leading%20up%20to%20Princess%20Diana's%20death%20were%20%26quot%3Bheavy%20and%20very%20manic%2C%20and%20incredibly%20invasive%26quot%3B%2C%20reports%20%3Cem%3EDeadline%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20show's%20sixth%20season%20will%20debut%20in%20two%20parts%20-%20on%20November%2016%20and%20December%2014%20-%20the%20first%20of%20which%20will%20cover%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20Diana's%20death%20and%20its%20devastating%20impact%20on%20her%20family%20and%20the%20monarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20difficult%20to%20recreate.%20At%20times%20it's%20almost%20like%20an%20animalistic%20response%20to%20being%20pursued%2C%20by%20that%20many%20actors%20playing%20the%20Press%2C%20because%20there's%20nowhere%20you%20can%20go%20and%20you%20only%20have%20to%20be%20in%20a%20situation%20like%20that%20for%20about%20a%20minute%20before%20you%20realise%20this%20is%20completely%20unbearable%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Debicki%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20no-one%20should%20ever%20be%20having%20to%20experience%20what%20it%20feels%20like%20to%20try%20and%20get%20the%20scenes%20in%20the%20daytime%20in%20Paris%2C%20trying%20to%20get%20from%20one%20place%20to%20another%2C%20and%20to%20have%20this%20swarm%20around%20you.%20Yo