arily%20depicts%20a%20wailing%20woman%20sitting%20next%20to%20bodies%20covered%20in%20shrouds.%20Two%20such%20bodies%20are%20visible%2C%20one%20possibly%20of%20a%20fully%20grown%20adult%20and%20another%20of%20a%20child.%20The%20footage%20had%20been%20seemingly%20aired%20by%20CNN%20first%2C%20following%20which%20Israeli%20news%20outlet%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.n12.co.il%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EN12%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0picked%20it%20up%20and%20zoomed%20into%20the%20footage%20and%20added%20a%20red%20circle%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20establish%20that%20the%20body%20was%20moving.%20The%20N12%20logo%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20viral%20video%20alongside%20the%20CNN%20logo.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20ascertaining%20that%20the%20viral%20video%20had%20been%20sourced%20from%20CNN%2C%20we%20located%20the%20corresponding%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Fvideos%2Fworld%2F2023%2F10%2F28%2Fgaza-hospital-nada-bashir-pkg-intl-vpx.cnn%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20featured%20the%20video.%20We%20observed%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98moving%20head%E2%80%99%20was%20not%20highlighted%20or%20circled%20in%20the%20original%20report.%20Below%20is%20a%20screen%20recording%20of%20the%20CNN%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20viral%20video%20can%20be%20seen%20from%20the%200%3A38-minute%20mark%20in%20the%20screen%20recording%20above.%20The%20burqa-clad%20woman%20can%20be%20seen%20grieving%20near%20the%20bodies%2C%20following%20which%20a%20man%20in%20a%20blue%20t-shirt%20sits%20beside%20her.%20He%20goes%20on%20to%20uncover%20the%20shroud%20from%20one%20of%20the%20deceased%20bodies.%20This%20is%20when%20the%20knot%20tied%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20corpse%20moves%2C%20making%20it%20seem%20like%20the%20body%20moved.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20found%20several%20instances%20in%20the%20CNN%20report%20of%20the%20man%20in%20the%20blue%20t-shirt%20helping%20families%20move%20dead%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20noted%20that%20the%20viral%20footage%20had%20been%20shot%20by%20Palestinian%20journalist%20Hassan%20Eslayeh%20on%20October%2028.%20We%20reached%20out%20to%20Hassan%2C%20who%20refuted%20the%20viral%20%E2%80%98fake%20dead%20body%E2%80%99%20claims%20and%20shared%20the%20unaltered%2C%20unedited%20video%20with%20us.%20Additionally%2C%20we%20were%20informed%20by%20Hassan%20that%20the%20woman%20seen%20in%20the%20video%20was%20mourning%20the%20loss%20of%20her%20son%2C%20whose%20body%20lay%20beneath%20the%20shroud.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20is%20evident%20from%20the%20aforementioned%20video%2C%20the%20man%20in%20the%20blue%20t-shirt%20moves%20part%20of%20the%20shroud%20to%20uncover%20the%20face%20of%20the%20corpse%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20knot%20moving.%C2%A0It%20is%20clear%20from%20this%20analysis%20that%20the%20head%20does%20not%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20sent%20us%20more%20pictures%20related%20to%20the%20viral%20footage%20that%20he%20had%20clicked%20on%20October%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20his%20photos%20show%20the%20same%20man%20and%20the%20woman%20sitting%20next%20to%20the%20deceased.%20In%20another%20image%2C%20the%20woman%20can%20be%20seen%20standing%20alongside%20three%20other%20people%20as%20three%20corpses%20lay%20in%20front%20of%20them.%20One%20image%20shows%20the%20woman%20grieving%20the%20loss%20of%20her%20loved%20one.%20See%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07132933%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-05-at-01.42.50-2.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07132933%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-0