E%20%3Cp%3EMrs%20Aayesha%20is%20in%20the%20fray%20as%20the%20ABVP's%20presidential%20candidate.%20Tarun%20Kumar%2C%20a%20research%20scholar%20from%20the%20School%20of%20Physics%2C%20is%20contesting%20the%20poll%20for%20the%20vice-president%20post.%20Rajesh%20Palia%2C%20a%20research%20scholar%20from%20the%20School%20of%20Economics%2C%20will%20fight%20for%20the%20role%20of%20general%20secretary.%20Rathod%20Vasanth%20Kumar%2C%20an%20Integrated%20MA%20student%20of%20Political%20Science%2C%20will%20vie%20for%20the%20position%20of%20joint%20secretary%20as%20a%20representative%20of%20SLVD.%20Antony%20Basumatary%2C%20a%20research%20scholar%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Philosophy%2C%20is%20running%20for%20the%20post%20of%20Cultural%20Secretary.%20Jwala%20Prasad%2C%20an%20Integrated%20MA%20student%20of%20Hindi%2C%20is%20in%20the%20race%20for%20the%20sports%20secretary%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EG%20Vinshika%20from%20IMA%20Sociology%20will%20contest%20for%20the%20ICC-GSCASH%20(Integrated)%20role.%20Aruna%20from%20M%20Optometry%20will%20run%20for%20the%20ICC-GSCASH%20(PG)%20position.%20Pawana%20from%20PhD%20Hindi%20will%20contend%20for%20the%20ICC-GSCASH%20(Research)%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ABVP%20Panel%20for%20the%20University%20of%20Hyderabad%20Union%20Elections%202023%20is%20all%20set%20to%20restore%20the%20dignity%20of%20students%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Hyderabad.%20The%20student%20community%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Hyderabad%20requires%20a%20student-centric%20Right%20to%20Union%2C%20for%20which%20the%20ABVP-SLVD%20is%20the%20only%20credible%20option%2C%20ensuring%20an%20accountable%2C%20responsive%2C%20and%20transparent%20UoHSU%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ABVP%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EABVP%20Panel%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FUoHSU2023%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_s