to%20be%20released%20in%20late%202024%2C%20giving%20fans%20more%20thrilling%20episodes%20to%20look%20forward%20to.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fsquid-game-2-actress-kim-si-eun-shares-her-experience-of-shooting-for-the-series-i-am-leaning-a-lot-on-the-set%2Farticleshow%2F105033702.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Was%20Totally%20Kept%20in%20Dark'%3A%20Congress's%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Writes%20to%20President%20on%20CIC%20Selection%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07131449%2FThe-Wire-69.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ECongress%20leader%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20has%20written%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20alleging%20that%20the%20government%20has%20%E2%80%9Ctotally%20kept%20%5Bhim%5D%20in%20the%20dark%E2%80%9D%20about%20the%20selection%20of%20Heeralal%20Samariya%20as%20the%20chief%20information%20commissioner%20(CIC).%20Samariya%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fheeralal-samariya-appointed-as-new-chief-information-commissioner%5C%22%3Eadministered%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20oath%20of%20office%20on%20Monday%2C%20November%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChowdhury%20is%20the%20representative%20from%20the%20opposition%20on%20the%20three-member%20high-powered%20selection%20committee%2C%20headed%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20constituted%20to%20appoint%20information%20commissioners%20and%20CIC.%20According%20to%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%2C%202005%2C%20the%20CIC%20and%20ICs%20are%20appointed%20by%20the%20President%20on%20the%20recommendation%20of%20this%20committee%2C%20comprising%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20(in%20this%20case%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20largest%20Opposition%20party)%20and%20a%20Union%20minister%20nominated%20by%20the%20prime%20minister.%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20the%20LoP%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20has%20been%20vacant%20since%202014%20on%20account%20of%20no%20party%20winning%20at%20least%2010%25%20of%20seats%20as%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20with%20extreme%20sadness%20and%20a%20heavy%20heart%20that%20I%20bring%20to%20your%20notice%20that%20all%20democratic%20norms%2C%20customs%2C%20and%20procedures%20were%20thrown%20to%20the%20wind%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20selection%20of%20the%20Central%20Information%20Commissioner%20and%20Information%20Commissioners%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20government%20neither%20consulted%20nor%20informed%20him%20about%20the%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWas%20totally%20kept%20in%20the%20dark%20about%20the%20selection%20of%20CIC%2FICs%E2%80%9D%3A%20Opposition%20leader%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20writes%20to%20President%20Murmu%20on%20Chief%20Information%20Commissioner%E2%80%99s%20appointment%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%F0%9F%93%B7%3A%20ANI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FttIfrzFU01%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FttIfrzFU01%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20NDTV%20(%40ndtv)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fndtv%2Fstatus%2F1721763180156715413%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%207%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fwas-kept-in-dark-on-appointment-of-new-cic-heeralal-samariya-adhir-writes-to-president-9016432%2F%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sources%20close%20to%20Chowdhury%20said%20the%20government%20communicated%20to%20him%20the%20meeting%20dates%20of%20the%20committee%20and%20later%20changed%20them%2C%20forcing%20him%20to%20change%20his%20schedule%20and%20his%20scheduled%20travel%20to%20Kolkata%20to%20be%20available%20for%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20meeting%20in%20Delhi.%20Despite%20that%2C%20they%20say%2C%20the%20selection%20of%20Samariya%E2%80%99s%20name%20has%20been%20announced%20without%20him%20being%20consulted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20(DoPT)%20had%20reached%20out%20to%20him%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20October%20seeking%20his%20availability%20for%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20meeting.%20His%20office%20informed%20them%20that%20he%20was%20available%20in%20Delhi%20until%20November%202%20and%20then%20he%20had%20to%20travel%20to%20West%20Bengal%20to%20attend%20a%20pre-scheduled%20meeting%20on%20November%203%2C%20Chowdhury%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20received%20communication%20from%20the%20DoPT%20telling%20him%20that%20the%20meeting%20had%20been%20scheduled%20for%206%20pm%20on%20November%203.%20Chowdhury%20then%20wrote%20to%20Union%20minister%20of%20personnel%2C%20public%20grievances%2C%20and%20pensions%2C%20Jitendra%20Singh%2C%20urging%20him%20to%20reschedule%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20for%20the%20schedule%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20my%20office%20was%20continuously%20in%20touch%20with%20officers%20concerned%20of%20the%20DoPT.%20It%20was%20informed%20in%20very%20clear%20terms%20that%20owing%20to%20a%20pre-scheduled%20function%20that%20I%20have%20to%20attend%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20it%20would%20not%20be%20possible%20for%20me%20to%20attend%20the%20meeting%20as%20per%20the%20schedule%20proposed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chowdhury%E2%80%99s%20letter%20dated%20November%201%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20requested%20that%20the%20meeting%20may%20be%20re-scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20on%201st%20or%202nd%20November%2C%202023%2C%20or%20at%209%20am%20on%203%20November%2C%202023%2C%20instead%20of%206%20pm%20on%20that%20day.%20As%20I%20am%20committed%20to%20attend%20the%20pre-scheduled%20meeting%20in%20the%20evening%20of%203%20November%2C%202023%2C%20I%20am%20compelled%20to%20express%20my%20inability%20to%20attend%20the%20meeting%20as%20per%20the%20schedule%20proposed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20thing%20that%20Chowdhury%20heard%20was%20that%20the%20government%20had%20gone%20ahead%20and%20appointed%20Samariya%20as%20the%20CIC%20without%20even%20informing%20him%20before%20making%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%2C%20despite%20being%20a%20member%20of%20the%20selection%20committee%20in%20my%20capacity%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20largest%20Opposition%20party%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20was%20totally%20kept%20in%20the%20dark%20about%20the%20selection%20of%20the%20CIC%2FICs%2C%20at%20the%20meeting%20that%20was%20held%20at%20the%20residence%20of%20the%20PM%2C%20November%203%2C%202023.%20The%20fact%20that%20within%20hours%20of%20the%20meeting%20in%20which%20only%20the%20PM%20and%20the%20Home%20Minister%20were%20present%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98face%20of%20the%20Opposition%E2%80%99%2C%20that%20is%2C%20me%2C%20as%20a%20bona%20fide%20member%20of%20the%20selection%20committee%20was%20not%20present%2C%20the%20names%20of%20the%20selected%20candidates%20were%20announced%2C%20notified%20and%20also%20sworn%20into%20office%2C%20only%20indicates%20that%20the%20entire%20selection%20exercise%20was%20predetermined%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20charged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20previous%20CIC%20Y.K.%20Sinha%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20on%20October%203%2C%20the%20post%20had%20been%20vacant%20until%20Samariya%E2%80%99s%20appointment.%20Before%20taking%20over%20as%20CIC%2C%20Samariya%20had%20been%20information%20commissioner%20since%20November%202020.%20Prior%20to%20that%2C%20he%20had%20served%20as%20labour%20and%20employment%20secretary%20in%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20Samariya%2C%20the%20government%20has%20also%20appointed%20Anandi%20Ramalingam%20and%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Tiwari%20as%20information%20commissioners.%20Ramalingam%20was%20serving%20as%20the%20chairman%20and%20managing%20director%20of%20Bharat%20Electronics%20Ltd%20prior%20to%20his%20latest%20appointment%2C%20and%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Tiwari%2C%20an%20Indian%20Forest%20Service%20officer%2C%20was%20holding%20the%20post%20of%20head%20of%20force-cum-principal%20chief%20conservator%20of%20forests%20as%20head%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20forest%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699344051000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07131449%2FThe-Wire-69.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwas-totally-kept-in-dark-congresss-adhir-ranjan-writes-to-president-on-cic-appointment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20representative%20of%20the%20opposition%20parties%20on%20the%20selection%20committee%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20said%20he%20was%20not%20consulted%20regarding%20the%20selection%20of%20Heeralal%20Samariya%20as%20the%20new%20chief%20information%20commissioner.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwas-totally-kept-in-dark-congresss-adhir-ranjan-writes-to-president-on-cic-appointment%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Odd-Even%20Rule%20Back%20In%20Delhi%20For%20A%20Week%20After%20Diwali%3A%20Check%20Guidelines%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Environment%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20on%20Monday%20said%20that%20the%20government%20will%20reintroduce%20the%20odd-even%20vehicle%20rationing%20system%20from%20November%2013%20to%2020.%20With%20stubble%20burning%20in%20Delhi's%20neighbouring%20states%20and%20only%20days%20to%20go%20for%20Diwali%20celebrations%2C%20the%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20continues%20to%20deteriorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20odd-even%20scheme%20will%20come%20into%20effect%20a%20day%20after%20Diwali%2C%20which%20falls%20on%20November%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Monday%2C%20Mr%20Rai%20said%20that%20the%20pollution%20is%20expected%20to%20worsen%20after%20Diwali.%20The%20minister%20explained%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20scheme%20has%20been%20enforced%20in%20Delhi%20before.%20On%20odd%20dates%2C%20vehicles%20with%20registration%20numbers%20ending%20in%201%2C%203%2C%205%2C%207%20and%209%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20ply.%20On%20even%20dates%2C%20vehicles%20with%20registration%20numbers%20ending%20in%200%2C%202%2C%204%2C%206%2C%208%20will%20run%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20odd-even%20scheme%20might%20get%20extended%2C%20based%20on%20the%20pollution%20level.%20During%20the%20restricted%20week%2C%20cars%20will%20be%20allowed%20on%20the%20roads%20only%20between%208%20a.m.%20and%208%20p.m.%20The%20odd-even%20rule%20applies%20to%20vehicles%20of%20other%20states%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Rai%20added%20that%20the%20government%20is%20making%20special%20arrangements%20for%20the%20ease%20of%20commuters%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOver%207%2C000%20buses%20are%20running%20in%20Delhi%2C%20out%20of%20which%201%2C000%20are%20electric.%20The%20frequency%20of%20buses%20and%20metros%20has%20also%20increased.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExceptions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20exceptions%20to%20the%20scheme%20are%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20CNG%20autos%2C%20emergency%20vehicles%2C%20and%20VVIP%20vehicles.%20Women-only%20cars%2C%20two-wheelers%2C%20vehicles%20on%20emergency%20duties%2C%20and%20cars%20having%20people%20with%20disabilities%20as%20occupants%20are%20exempted%2C%20says%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fdelhis-aqi-crisis-the-revival-of-the-odd-even-scheme-key-information-you-should-know-11677561.html%5C%22%3EMoney%20Control.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20details%20about%20the%20exceptions%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20revealed%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFlouting%20the%20odd-even%20norms%20entailed%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20when%20the%20scheme%20was%20first%20introduced%20in%202016.%20However%2C%20in%202019%20the%20fine%20was%20raised%20to%20Rs%204%2C000.%20The%20Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%20is%20authorised%20to%20enforce%20the%20scheme%20and%20impose%20the%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20Odd-even%20scheme%2C%20the%20government%20has%20also%20instructed%20schools%20to%20suspend%20physical%20classes%2C%20except%20for%20students%20of%20classes%2010%20and%2012%2C%20until%20November%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699343940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-04%2F6sfln5v_odd-even_650x400_19_April_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-odd-even-scheme-delhi-to-implement-odd-even-scheme-after-diwali-all-you-need-to-know-4552817%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Environment%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20on%20Monday%20said%20that%20the%20government%20will%20reintroduce%20the%20odd-even%20vehicle%20rationing%20system%20from%20November%2013%20to%2020.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-odd-even-scheme-delhi-to-implement-odd-even-scheme-after-diwali-all-you-need-to-know-4552817%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-odd-even-scheme-delhi-to-implement-odd-even-scheme-after-diwali-all-you-need-to-know-4552817%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-odd-even-scheme-delhi-to-implement-odd-even-scheme-after-diwali-all-you-need-to-know-4552817%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22WeWork%20forced%20to%20file%20for%20bankruptcy%20in%20the%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699343841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FD645%2Fproduction%2F_131635845_wework_index_1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-67316150%22%2C%22summary%22