Campus%20Starts%20First%20Batch%20With%20These%20Courses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%20Madras%20inaugurated%20the%20first%20ever%20international%20campus%20of%20IIT%20in%20Zanzibar%2C%20Africa%20on%20November%206.%20The%20institute%20set%20off%20with%20the%20first%20batch%20of%20courses%20in%20Bachelor%20of%20Science%20(BS)%20and%20MTech%20programmes.%20More%20academic%20programmes%20will%20be%20launched%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20batch%20at%20IITM%20Zanzibar%20comprises%20of%20students%20from%20Zanzibar%2C%20mainland%20Tanzania%2C%20Nepal%20and%20India%20with%2040%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20students%20being%20women.%20A%20total%20of%2045%20students%20have%20been%20admitted%20for%20a%20four-year%20Bachelor%20of%20Science%20degree%20in%20Data%20Science%20and%20AI%20and%20a%20two-year%20Master%20of%20Technology%20degree%20in%20Data%20Science%20and%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Zanzibar%20campus%20was%20inaugurated%20by%20His%20Excellency%20Dr%20Hussein%20Ali%20Mwinyi%2C%20President%20of%20Zanzibar%20and%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Revolutionary%20Council%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Tanzanian%20officials%2C%20Indian%20dignitaries%2C%20faculty%20and%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20campus%20was%20inaugurated%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Prof%20Adolf%20F%20Mkenda%2C%20Minister%20of%20Education%20Science%20and%20Technology%20United%20Republic%20of%20Tanzania%2C%20Hon%20Binaya%20Srikanta%20Pradhan%2C%20India%20High%20Commissioner%20of%20The%20United%20Republic%20of%20Tanzania%2C%20Lela%20Mohamed%20Mussa%2C%20Minister%20of%20Education%20and%20Vocational%20Training-Zanzibar%2C%20Prof%20M%20S%20Ananth%20and%20Prof%20Bhaskar%20Ramamurthi%2C%20former%20Directors%20of%20IIT%20Madras%2C%20Prof%20Preeti%20Aghalayam%2C%20Dean%20of%20School%20of%20Engineering%20and%20Science%2C%20and%20Director-in-charge%2C%20Zanzibar%20campus%2C%20IIT%20Madras%2C%20faculty%2C%20students%2C%20staff%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20campus%20has%20been%20launched%20with%20the%20government's%20aim%20to%20take%20top%20quality%20education%20system%20of%20India%20to%20international%20arenas.%20The%20campus%20has%20been%20built%20in%20Bweleo%20district%2C%20located%20approximately%2015%20km%20south%20of%20Zanzibar%20town%20and%20is%20equipped%20with%20international%20amenities%20designed%20to%20meet%20the%20current%20needs%20of%20students.%20A%20permanent%20campus%20will%20be%20built%20soon%20jointly%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20Zanzibar%20and%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20campus%20has%20been%20designed%20to%20accommodate%20students%20in%20dorms%20and%20provide%20various%20facilities%20such%20as%20offices%2C%20classrooms%20and%20auditoriums%2C%20dining%20and%20a%20dispensary.%20Besides%20this%2C%20sports%20facilities%20are%20being%20planned%20at%20the%20institute.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20initiative%2C%20V%20Kamakoti%2C%20director%2C%20IIT%20Madras%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20programmes%20at%20IIT%20Madras%20Zanzibar%20are%20open%20to%20students%20of%20all%20nationalities%2C%20including%20Indians.%20Apart%20from%20a%20comprehensive%20curriculum%20that%20includes%20all%20aspects%20of%20Data%20Science%20and%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2C%20students%20will%20have%20access%20to%20several%20interesting%20opportunities%20during%20their%20course%20of%20study.%20These%20include%20study%20abroad%2Fsemester%20exchange%20programmes%20with%20IIT%20Madras'%20partner%20institutions%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20Australia%2C%20among%20other%20countries%2C%20internships%20with%20various%20relevant%20companies%20and%20a%20chance%20to%20meet%20some%20of%20the%20course%20requirements%20at%20the%20IIT%20Madras%20campus%20in%20Chennai%2C%20India.%20Classes%20for%20the%20first%20academic%20year%20(2023-24)%20commenced%20in%20October%202023.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Office%20of%20Global%20Engagement%2C%20IIT%20Madras%2C%20coo