ess-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-today-nov-7-nse-bse-sensex-nifty-bajaj-finance-nykaa-q2-hpcl-oil-cipla-123110700100_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stock%20market%20LIVE%20updates%20on%20November%207%2C%202023%3A%20Bajaj%20twins%2C%20Sun%20Pharma%2C%20IndusInd%20Bank%20and%20Wipro%20were%20the%20top%20Sensex%20gainers%2C%20while%20ICICI%20Bank%2C%20HDFC%20Bank%2C%20Tata%20Steel%2C%20and%20Power%20Grid%20fell%20the%20most%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-today-nov-7-nse-bse-sensex-nifty-bajaj-finance-nykaa-q2-hpcl-oil-cipla-123110700100_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-today-nov-7-nse-bse-sensex-nifty-bajaj-finance-nykaa-q2-hpcl-oil-cipla-123110700100_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-today-nov-7-nse-bse-sensex-nifty-bajaj-finance-nykaa-q2-hpcl-oil-cipla-123110700100_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20New%20Biography%20Outlines%20the%20Contradictions%20in%20His%20Life%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F02102823%2F46339127625_054ddd1a61_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%2C%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20richest%20man%2C%20has%20his%20fingers%20in%20many%20pies%2C%20none%20of%20them%20your%20standard%20Four%20and%20Twenty%20%E2%80%93%20space%20exploration%2C%20electric%20cars%2C%20AI%20and%20social%20media%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20became%20a%20global%20leader%20in%20space%20exploration%20when%20NASA%20had%20virtually%20vacated%20the%20field%2C%20and%20his%20electric%20vehicle%20company%20Tesla%2C%20headquartered%20in%20the%20gas-guzzling%20United%20States%2C%20has%20by%20far%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.usnews.com%2Finvesting%2Farticles%2Fthe-10-most-valuable-auto-companies-in-the-world%5C%22%3Ebiggest%20market%20capitalisation%20of%20any%20car%20manufacturer%20in%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20yet%20he%20has%20few%20formal%20qualifications%20in%20either%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20see%20Musk%20as%20a%2021st-century%20idiot%20savant.%20Others%2C%20watching%20him%20reduce%20an%20important%20social%20media%20platform%20%E2%80%93%20Twitter%20%E2%80%93%20to%20cyber-rubble%2C%20think%20of%20him%20simply%20as%20an%20idiot.%20Maybe%20both%20are%20true%2C%20or%20maybe%20other%20readings%20of%20his%20life%20are%20true.%20Aged%2052%2C%20Musk%20certainly%20merits%20a%20good%2C%20searching%20biography.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWalter%20Isaacson%20seems%20well%20credentialed%20for%20the%20task.%20He%20has%20written%20biographies%20of%20Henry%20Kissinger%2C%20Benjamin%20Franklin%2C%20Albert%20Einstein%2C%20Steve%20Jobs%20and%20Leonardo%20da%20Vinci%20that%20have%20won%20awards%20or%20become%20bestsellers%2C%20or%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20325px)%2085vw%2C%20325px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07095625%2F440px-Walter_Isaacson_VF_2012_Shankbone_2-240x300.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22325%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07095625%2F440px-Walter_Isaacson_VF_2012_Shankbone_2-240x300.jpeg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07095625%2F440px-Walter_Isaacson_VF_2012_Shankbone_2.jpeg%20440w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683817%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22406%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWalter%20Isaacson%2C%20Photo%3A%20David%20Shankbone%2C%20CC%20BY%203.0%2C%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsaacson%20began%20his%20working%20life%20as%20a%20journalist.%20He%20spent%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20at%20%3Cem%3ETime%3C%2Fem%3E%20during%20the%20magazine%E2%80%99s%20heyday%2C%20rising%20to%20become%20editor%20in%201996.%20Since%20then%2C%20he%20has%20been%20chief%20executive%20of%20the%20CNN%20cable%20television%20network%2C%20headed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aspeninstitute.org%2F%5C%22%3EAspen%20Institute%3C%2Fa%3E%20(a%20longstanding%20non-profit%20think%20tank)%2C%20become%20a%20professor%20of%20history%20at%20Tulane%20University%2C%20and%20done%20various%20jobs%20for%20both%20Republican%20and%20Democrat%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20he%20was%20awarded%20the%20National%20Humanities%20Medal%20by%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsaacson%E2%80%99s%20virtue%20as%20a%20biographer%20is%20his%20reporter%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20gather%20enormous%20amounts%20of%20material%20and%20quickly%20render%20it%20as%20a%20(generally)%20smooth%20and%20readable%20account%20of%20a%20life%20bursting%20with%20dramatic%20events.%20His%20project%20only%20began%20in%202021%20and%20covers%20events%20up%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F04%2F20%2Fworld%2Fspacex-starship-launch-thursday-scn%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ESpace%20X%E2%80%99s%20unsuccessful%20Starship%20rocket%20launch%20in%20April%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMusk%20made%20himself%20available%20for%20numerous%20interviews.%20He%20gave%20Isaacson%20access%20to%20places%20and%20people%20at%20key%20moments%2C%20such%20as%20the%20purchase%20of%20Twitter%20(now%20known%20as%20X)%2C%20and%20regularly%20emailed%20Isaacson%20at%203am%20with%20his%20thoughts%20%E2%80%93%20and%20thought%20bubbles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsaacson%20also%20interviewed%20130%20other%20people%2C%20and%20his%20labours%20have%20uncovered%20newsworthy%20information%20that%20has%20been%20widely%20reported%20%E2%80%93%20and%2C%20in%20one%20case%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fbooks%2F2023%2F09%2F10%2Felon-musk-walter-isaacson-biography-review%2F%5C%22%3Ecorrected%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20since%20the%20book%E2%80%99s%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Isaacson%20builds%20on%20earlier%20reporting%20by%20the%20Washington%20Post%20to%20reveal%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20Musk%E2%80%99s%20Starlink%20satellite%20network%20has%20been%20crucial%20to%20the%20Ukrainian%20military%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20fight%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20invasion%2C%20providing%20them%20with%20continued%20access%20to%20the%20internet%20on%20the%20battlefield%20after%20the%20Russians%20destroyed%20access%20to%20other%20internet%20services.%20He%20shows%20how%20Musk%20was%20persuaded%20by%20the%20Russians%20to%20temporarily%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2023%2Fsep%2F07%2Felon-musk-ordered-starlink-turned-off-ukraine-offensive-biography%5C%22%3Ecut%20off%20the%20Starlink%20access%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20he%20believed%20their%20entreaties%20that%20any%20further%20victories%20by%20Ukraine%20would%20provoke%20nuclear%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20implications%20of%20these%20remarkable%20revelations%20have%20been%20examined%20by%20the%20ABC%E2%80%99s%20Matt%20Bevan%20in%20a%20recent%20episode%20of%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Flisten%2Fprograms%2Fif-youre-listening%2Fshould-elon-musk-have-stopped-ukraine-attacking-russia-%2F102929348%5C%22%3EIf%20You%E2%80%99re%20Listening%3C%2Fa%3E%20podcast.%20But%20even%20though%20Isaacson%20revealed%20this%20information%2C%20he%20does%20not%20pause%20to%20discuss%20it%20in%20any%20detail.%20That%E2%80%99s%20one%20of%20the%20shortcomings%20of%20this%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELord%20of%20the%20Flies%20on%20steroids%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20seduced%20by%20Musk%E2%80%99s%20apparent%20candour%20or%20a%20publisher%E2%80%99s%20pressure%20to%20rush%20to%20print%2C%20Isaacson%20accepts%20his%20subject%E2%80%99s%20words%20without%20sufficient%20scepticism.%20For%20instance%2C%20Musk%E2%80%99s%20childhood%20experiences%20at%20a%20veldskool%20in%201970s%20South%20Africa%20read%20like%20Lord%20of%20the%20Flies%20on%20steroids.%20Bullying%20was%20the%20norm%20and%20children%20were%20encouraged%20to%20fight%20over%20meagre%20food%20rations.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20few%20years%2C%20one%20of%20the%20kids%20would%20die%2C%E2%80%9D%20writes%20Isaacson.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReally%3F%20Says%20who%3F%20Musk%2C%20apparently.%20No%20one%20from%20the%20school%20is%20listed%20in%20the%20source%20notes%2C%20to%20confirm%20or%20refute%20this%20account.%20Throughout%20the%20book%2C%20Musk%20comes%20off%20as%20a%20shameless%20self-dramatiser%2C%20but%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20his%20biographer%20should%20succumb%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsaacson%20is%20an%20adherent%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgrand%20man%E2%80%9D%20school%20of%20history.%20He%20has%20written%20only%20one%20biography%20of%20a%20woman%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Nobel%20Prize-winning%20biochemist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nobelprize.org%2Fprizes%2Fchemistry%2F2020%2Fdoudna%2Ffacts%2F%5C%22%3EJennifer%20Doudna%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20is%20far%20less%20interested%20in%2C%20or%20comfortable%20with%2C%20the%20role%20structures%20and%20systems%20play%20in%20shaping%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorker.com%2Fmagazine%2F2023%2F09%2F18%2Felon-musk-walter-isaacson-book-review%5C%22%3EJill%20Lepore%20pointed%20out%20in%20the%20New%20Yorker%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Isaacson%20also%20has%20%E2%80%9Can%20executive%E2%80%99s%20affinity%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.investopedia.com%2Fterms%2Fc%2Fc-suite.asp%5C%22%3EC-suite%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20meaning%20he%20pays%20little%20attention%20to%20the%20people%20who%20work%20for%20Musk%20or%20the%20impact%20of%20his%20actions%20on%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20core%20question%20driving%20the%20biography%20is%3A%20has%20Elon%20Musk%20had%20to%20be%20such%20an%20%E2%80%9Casshole%E2%80%9D%20(Isaacson%E2%80%99s%20term)%20to%20achieve%20what%20he%20has%3F%20Isaacson%20acknowledges%20it%20is%20much%20the%20same%20question%20he%20asked%20about%20Steve%20Jobs%20in%20his%20earlier%20biography%20of%20the%20Apple%20cofounder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20lost%20count%20of%20the%20times%20the%20question%2C%20or%20a%20variation%20of%20it%2C%20was%20posed%20during%20the%20book%E2%80%99s%20670%20pages%2C%20but%20in%20classic%20Time-style%20both-sidesing%2C%20Isaacson%20keeps%20toggling%20between%20admonishing%20Musk%20for%20behaving%20like%20an%20%E2%80%9Casshole%E2%80%9D%20and%20admiring%20his%20ability%20to%20get%20results.%20He%20rarely%20if%20ever%20lifts%20his%20gaze%20beyond%20this%20binary%2C%20which%20means%20he%20ignores%20lessons%20learned%20from%20all%20those%20people%2C%20past%20and%20present%2C%20who%20have%20achieved%20things%20without%20treating%20people%20appallingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20means%20achievements%20are%20seen%20solely%20through%20the%20prism%20of%20one%20person%E2%80%99s%20actions.%20In%20a%20perceptive%20article%20in%20Vox%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fculture%2F23872485%2Felon-musk-walter-isaacson-biography-review%5C%22%3EConstance%20Grady%3C%2Fa%3E%20reminds%20us%20that%20Musk%E2%80%99s%20determination%20to%20override%20safety%20concerns%20in%20Tesla%20factories%20has%20led%20to%20worker%20injury%20rates%20equivalent%20to%20those%20in%20a%20slaughterhouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGrady%20allows%20that%20Isaacson%20reports%20the%20increased%20injury%20rates%2C%20but%20notes%20his%20vagueness%20about%20exactly%20what%20kind%20of%20injuries%20occurred.%20Citing%202018%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frevealnews.org%2Farticle%2Ftesla-says-its-factory-is-safer-but-it-left-injuries-off-the-books%2F%5C%22%3Ework%20by%20the%20Center%20for%20Investigative%20Reporting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20reveals%20Tesla%20workers%20were%20%E2%80%9Csliced%20by%20machinery%2C%20crushed%20by%20forklifts%2C%20burned%20in%20electrical%20explosions%2C%20and%20sprayed%20with%20molten%20metal%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20notes%20Isaacson%20downplaying%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20experience%20of%20COVID-19.%20Musk%2C%20a%20fervent%20libertarian%20allergic%20to%20any%20form%20of%20regulation%2C%20kept%20the%20factory%20running%20during%20the%20global%20pandemic.%20Isaacson%20says%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20factory%20experienced%20no%20serious%20COVID%20outbreak%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20Grady%20reports%20there%20were%20450%20positive%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20Twitter%20to%20X%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20an%20immense%20work%20ethic%20and%20expects%20everyone%20working%20for%20him%20to%20share%20it.%20By%20relentlessly%20questioning%20all%20assumptions%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20laws%20of%20physics%20are%20unbreakable%3B%20everything%20else%20is%20a%20recommendation%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20Musk%20and%20those%20working%20in%20his%20companies%20have%20indeed%20achieved%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20am%20not%20really%20in%20any%20position%20to%20assess%20Musk%E2%80%99s%20contribution%20to%20space%20exploration%2C%20AI%20or%20car%20manufacturing.%20But%20I%20am%20willing%20to%20accept%20the%20evidence%20of%20Isaacson%E2%80%99s%20biography%20that%20they%20have%20been%20substantial%20%E2%80%93%20or%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20AI%2C%20promise%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27151659%2FF1yPk5VXoAA3rGZ.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27151659%2FF1yPk5VXoAA3rGZ.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27151659%2FF1yPk5VXoAA3rGZ-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27151659%2FF1yPk5VXoAA3rGZ-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665449%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Twitter%2FX%20headquarters%20on%20July%2024.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40elonmusk%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20better%20able%20to%20assess%20Musk%E2%80%99s%20contribution%20to%20social%20media.%20Here%2C%20the%20evidence%20presented%20by%20Isaacson%20and%20many%20others%20is%20that%20Musk%20has%20damaged%2C%20perhaps%20irretrievably%2C%20Twitter%20%E2%80%93%20which%20he%20has%20renamed%20X%2C%20a%20letter%20of%20the%20alphabet%20to%20which%20he%20seems%20inordinately%20attached.%20Not%20only%20has%20he%20named%20one%20of%20his%20children%20X%2C%20he%20waves%20away%20the%20letter%E2%80%99s%20other%20connotations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201999%2C%20Musk%20cofounded%20the%20online%20bank%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FX.com_(bank)%5C%22%3EX.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20soon%20learned%20there%20was%20another%20company%20aimed%20at%20revolutionising%20online%20transactions%2C%20PayPal%2C%20founded%20at%20around%20the%20same%20time%20by%20Peter%20Thiel%2C%20Max%20Levchin%20and%20Luke%20Nosek.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20merged%20in%202000%2C%20amid%20a%20classic%20Silicon%20Valley%20phallus-waving%20struggle%20over%20who%20had%20the%20idea%20first%20and%20who%20should%20take%20over%20whom.%20Levchin%20derided%20X.com%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cseedy%20site%20you%20would%20not%20talk%20about%20in%20polite%20company%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20want%20to%20take%20over%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20financial%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20Musk%20rebutted%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthen%20X%20is%20the%20better%20name.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMusk%20lost%20the%20nomenclature%20war%20then%2C%20but%20realised%20his%20dream%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20later%20when%20he%20bought%20Twitter%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F10%2F27%2Ftechnology%2Felon-musk-twitter-deal-complete.html%5C%22%3EUS%2444%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20could%20call%20it%20whatever%20he%20liked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpulsive%2C%20determined%2C%20clueless%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20picture%20of%20Musk%20that%20emerges%20in%20Isaacson%E2%80%99s%20book%20is%20of%20an%20impulsive%2C%20utterly%20determined%20person%20who%20is%20genuinely%20talented%20as%20a%20physicist%20and%20businessperson%2C%20and%20genuinely%20clueless%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20human%20relationships.%20He%20either%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20get%20people%20or%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20care%20about%20them%20%E2%80%93%20or%2C%20more%20likely%2C%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20dotes%20on%20his%20children%2C%20especially%20X%20(I%20guess%20you%20need%20to%20do%20something%20to%20compensate%20for%20naming%20a%20child%20after%20a%20letter)%2C%20yet%20he%20is%20capable%20of%20breathtaking%20callousness%20and%20rank%20sexism.%20He%20whispered%20in%20his%20first%20wife%E2%80%99s%20ear%20on%20their%20wedding%20night%20that%20he%20was%20the%20alpha%20male%20in%20the%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Musk%E2%80%99s%20third%20wife%2C%20Shivon%20Zilis%2C%20was%20pregnant%20with%20twins%20conceived%20with%20Musk%20by%20in-vitro%20fertilisation%2C%20and%20was%20in%20a%20hospital%20in%20Texas%20experiencing%20complications.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20and%20in%20the%20same%20hospital%2C%20a%20woman%20serving%20as%20a%20surrogate%20for%20Musk%20and%20his%20ex-wife%2C%20Claire%20Boucher%20%E2%80%93%20better%20known%20as%20the%20Canadian-born%20musician%20Grimes%20%E2%80%93%20was%20also%20experiencing%20pregnancy%20complications.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EZilis%20and%20Boucher%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20surrogate%2C%20did%20not%20know%20about%20the%20other%E2%80%99s%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Isaacson%20drolly%20comments%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20book%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20developed%20an%20aura%20that%20made%20him%20seem%2C%20at%20times%2C%20like%20an%20alien%2C%20as%20if%20his%20Mars%20mission%20were%20an%20aspiration%20to%20return%20home%2C%20and%20his%20desire%20to%20build%20humanoid%20robots%20were%20a%20quest%20for%20kinship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3EMusk%20is%20on%20record%20saying%20humanity%20is%20in%20danger%20of%20not%20having%20enough%20smart%20people%20and%20it%20is%20his%20duty%20to%20populate%20the%20planet%20with%20as%20many%20of%20them%20as%20possible.%20To%20date%2C%20he%20has%2011%20children.%20If%20that%20notion%20sounds%20disturbingly%20like%20eugenics%2C%20it%20is%20not%20something%20Isaacson%20reflects%20on%20as%20he%20studiously%20documents%20Musk%E2%80%99s%20chaotic%20love%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENor%20does%20he%20delay%20his%20rat-a-tat-tat%20narration%20of%20every%20twist%20and%20turn%20in%20Musk%E2%80%99s%20dramatic%20life%20to%20question%20his%20subject%E2%80%99s%20burning%20desire%20to%20make%20humanity%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmulti-planet%20civilisation%E2%80%9D%20by%20colonising%20Mars.%20Musk%20is%20obsessed%20with%20this%20goal%20because%20he%20is%20worried%20about%20the%20prospect%20of%20our%20planet%20being%20destroyed%20by%20the%20accelerating%20consequences%20of%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20laudable%20ambition%2C%20no%20doubt.%20But%20neither%20he%20nor%20his%20biographer%20stops%20to%20ask%3A%20if%20humanity%20fails%20so%20badly%20that%20it%20destroys%20this%20world%2C%20why%20would%20you%20think%20it%20could%20make%20life%20better%20on%20another%2C%20already%20inhospitable%20planet%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStartling%20achievements%20and%20childish%20petulance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20easy%20and%20tempting%20to%20poke%20fun%20at%20Musk.%20Perhaps%20this%20is%20because%20his%20personality%20combines%20grandiose%20visions%20with%20arrested%20development%2C%20startling%20achievements%20with%20childish%20petulance.%20His%20idea%20of%20dieting%20is%20to%20get%20hold%20of%20the%20diabetes%20medication%20Ozempic%20%E2%80%93%20the%20dieter%E2%80%99s%20drug%20du%20jour%20%E2%80%93%20begin%20an%20intermittent%20fasting%20regime%2C%20then%20make%20his%20first%20meal%20of%20the%20day%20a%20bacon-and-cheese%20burger%20and%20sweet-potato%20fries%20topped%20with%20a%20cookie-dough%20ice-cream%20milkshake.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOr%20do%20you%20remember%20how%20Musk%20responded%20in%202018%20to%20a%20mild%20rebuke%20of%20his%20frenetic%20desire%20to%20play%20the%20hero%20rescuing%20children%20trapped%20in%20a%20cave%20in%20Thailand%20with%20a%20purpose-built%20mini-craft%3F%20That%E2%80%99s%20right%2C%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2018%2Fjul%2F15%2Felon-musk-british-diver-thai-cave-rescue-pedo-twitter%5C%22%3Elabelling%20one%20of%20the%20actual%20rescuers%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpedo%20guy%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20is%20dangerously%20easy.%20Social%20media%20plays%20an%20important%20role%20in%20modern%20society.%20Whatever%20its%20benefits%2C%20and%20they%20are%20many%2C%20the%20algorithms%20embedded%20in%20social%20media%20platforms%20%E2%80%93%20by%20their%20owners%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20not%20forget%20%E2%80%93%20neatly%20sidestep%20nuance%20and%20reason%20in%20debate%2C%20turbo-charge%20conflict%20and%20emotion%2C%20and%20play%20a%20role%20in%20the%20spread%20of%20misinformation%20and%20disinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090130%2F33486317444_675767e767_o.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090130%2F33486317444_675767e767_o.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090130%2F33486317444_675767e767_o-300x223.jpg%20300w%2C