0contesting%20the%20election%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20tough%20fight%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20villager%20from%20Gidam%20%3Cem%3Etehsil%3C%2Fem%3E%20said.%20In%20Dantewada%2C%20Chhavindra%20Karma%20has%20the%20advantage%20of%20various%20factors%20working%20in%20his%20favour%2C%20including%20sympathy%20of%20being%20a%20Karma%20family%20scion%20who%20is%20taking%20his%20late%20father%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EKondagaon%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20had%20won%20with%20a%20mere%20margin%20of%201%2C796%20votes%20in%202018%2C%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20tough%20battlefield%20for%20both%20the%20major%20parties.%20The%20competition%20is%20between%20Congress%20MLA%20Mohan%20Markam%2C%20the%20ex-Pradesh%20Congress%20chief%2C%20and%20BJP%20national%20vice%20president%20Lata%20Usendi.%20With%20tough%20tribal%20sentiments%20against%20Markam%2C%20his%20seat%20is%20stuck%20in%20a%20neck-to-neck%20competition%2C%20much%20like%20the%20last%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20Antagarh%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20won%20in%202018%20with%20a%20margin%20of%2013%2C414%20votes.%20However%2C%20the%20Congress%20chose%20a%20new%20candidate%2C%20angering%20the%20existing%20MLA%2C%20Anoop%20Nag%2C%20who%20has%20decided%20to%20contest%20election%20independently.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20party%20chose%20some%20random%20survey%20over%20their%20own%20workers%E2%80%99%20hard%20work.%20They%20will%20realise%20their%20mistake%20in%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAcross%20Bastar%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20also%20seeing%20strong%20anti-tribal%20sentiments.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20tribals%20had%20trusted%20Congress.%20We%20were%20fooled%20on%20every%20step.%20The%20Congress%20government%20brought%20in%20a%20diluted%20PESA%20%5BPanchayats%20(Extension%20to%20Scheduled%20Areas)%20Act%5D%20law%2C%20made%20tribal%20politics%20obsolete%20in%20the%20OBC%20wave%20and%20helmed%20decisions%20that%20were%20similar%20to%20the%20BJP%20when%20it%20came%20to%20dealing%20with%20maoists.%20Innocent%20tribals%20are%20still%20being%20prosecuted%2C%20they%20are%20still%20languishing%20in%20jail.%20The%20Congress%20disappointed%20the%20tribals%20just%20like%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20Sarva%20Adiwasi%20Samaj%20official%20said%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Sarva%20Adiwasi%20Samaj%20has%20launched%20a%20%E2%80%9CHamar%20Raj%E2%80%9D%20party%2C%20who%20have%20launched%20candidates%20across%20all%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20hope%20our%20candidates%20win.%20But%20even%20otherwise%2C%20we%20will%20surely%20damage%20the%20vote%20count%20for%20the%20parties%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchhattisgarh-in-chandameta-with-electricity-roads-and-water-a-polling-booth-for-the-first-time%5C%22%3EChhattisgarh%3A%20In%20Chandameta%2C%20With%20Electricity%2C%20Roads%20and%20Water%20%E2%80%93%20a%20Polling%20Booth%20for%20the%20First%20Time%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20most%20interesting%20election%20in%20the%20Bastar%20region%2C%20however%2C%20is%20being%20fought%20in%20Sukma%2C%20one%20of%20the%20still%20red%20districts%20in%20the%20red%20corridor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20Sukma%20district%E2%80%99s%20Konta%2C%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20Kawasi%20Lakhma%20is%20facing%20stiff%20opposition%20from%20his%20constituency.%20The%20cabinet%20minister%20has%20had%20to%20face%20severe%20criticism%20in%20Konta%20over%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20various%20protests%2C%20including%20Silger%2C%20which%20lasted%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year.%20On%20May%2017%2C%202021%2C%20four%20tribals%20were%20shot%20dead%20by%20security%20forces%20after%20they%20opened%20fire%20on%20a%20protesting%20mob.%20The%20mob%20of%20residents%20from%20nearby%20villages%20were%20protesting%20against%20a%20security%20camp.%20While%20police%20maintained%20that%20the%20protests%20were%20on%20the%20behest%20of%20Maoists%2C%20the%20locals%20protested%20on%20the%20site%20of%20conflict%20in%20huge%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F05%2F17105859%2FScreenshot-2022-05-17-at-10.58.13-AM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F05%2F17105859%2FScreenshot-2022-05-17-at-10.58.13-AM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F05%2F17105859%2FScreenshot-2022-05-17-at-10.58.13-AM-300x190.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F05%2F17105859%2FScreenshot-2022-05-17-at-10.58.13-AM-1024x648.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-597022%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22759%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFile%20image%20of%20a%202022%20protest%20march%20at%20Silger%2C%20in%20Sukma%20of%20Chhattisgarh.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20election%2C%20the%20prominent%20candidate%20from%20Sukma%20was%20Manish%20Kunjam%2C%20an%20ex-MLA%20from%20CPI.%20While%20his%20rallies%20were%20drawing%20many%20people%20he%20had%20alleged%20that%20the%20district%20machinery%20had%20been%20trying%20to%20stop%20him%20from%20visiting%20villages%2C%20citing%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20reasons%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20are%20there%20so%20many%20camps%20if%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20provide%20me%20enough%20security%20to%20meet%20the%20villagers%2C%20like%20common%20men%3F%20It%20is%20a%20planned%20mission%20of%20the%20MLA%20along%20with%20district%20officials%2C%20to%20stop%20me%20reaching%20parts%20of%20my%20constituency%20where%20people%20are%20full%20of%20anger%20against%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EKunjam%2C%20however%2C%20faced%20the%20first%20fall%20after%20his%20party%20symbol%20was%20changed%20from%20the%20CPI%E2%80%99s%20well%20known%20hammer%20and%20sickle%20to%20an%20air%20conditioner.%20The%20symbol%20was%20allotted%20to%20him%20after%20the%20party%20realised%20that%20they%20had%20forgotten%20to%20fill%20in%20some%20pre-election%20paperwork.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20still%20fighting%20on%20my%20name%20and%20my%20outreach.%20We%20have%20faith%20in%20the%20public%E2%80%99s%20judgement%2C%20we%20will%20win%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20Konta%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20another%20Judum%20face%2C%20Soyam%20Muka%2C%20who%20has%20a%20good%20rapport%20with%20tribal%20sub-groups%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20BJP%20candidate%20has%20spent%20considerable%20time%20in%20attending%20the%20various%20%3Cem%3Ekalash%20yatra%3C%2Fem%3Es%20and%20%3Cem%3Ehavan%3C%2Fem%3Es%20organised%20by%20various%20groups%20in%20the%20suburban%20region%20of%20Sukma.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20Sarva%20Adiwasi%20Samaj%20in%20Sukma%20has%20been%20continuously%20resisting%20attempts%20at%20Hinduisation%2C%20by%20refusing%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20state%20wide%20Ramkatha%20tournament%20amongst%20other%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Bastar%2C%20the%20government%20schemes%20are%20not%20as%20pertinent%20as%20they%20are%20in%20the%20plains.%20While%20competition%20is%20neck%20to%20neck%20in%20seats%20like%20Bijapur%2C%20Jagdalpur%3B%20some%20seats%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20anger%20for%20the%20Congress%20party%20like%20Chitrakot%20and%20Narayanpur.%20The%20tribal%20votes%20as%20well%20as%20Christian%20votes%20will%20not%20benefit%20the%20Congress%20as%20it%20did%20the%20last%20time.%20But%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20keen%20on%20BJP%20either.%20Some%20votes%20will%20get%20diverted%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20this%20election%20will%20be%20choosing%20the%20lesser%20of%20two%20evils%20for%20many%20constituencies%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20political%20functionary%20said%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699331315000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F05%2F17105859%2FScreenshot-2022-05-17-at-10.58.13-AM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fanti-bjp-anti-congress-where-the-tussle-lies-in-bastar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'In%20Bastar%2C%20the%20government%20schemes%20are%20not%20as%20pertinent%20as%20they%20are%20in%20the%20plains%2C'%20as%20a%20political%20worker%20puts%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fanti-bjp-anti-congress-where-the-tussle-lies-in-bastar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2235%20elephants%20suddenly%20dropped%20dead%20in%202020.%20Their%20case%20has%20finally%20been%20solved.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Silhouette%20of%20elephant%20in%20tall%20grass%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654993f13cc84b4dfafd754f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJeremy%20Woodhouse%2FGetty%20images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIn%202020%2C%2035%20elephants%20dropped%20dead%20in%20Zimbabwe%20over%20a%20month%20timespan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere%20were%20no%20signs%20of%20external%20trauma%20or%20intentional%20poisoning.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20scientists%20said%20they%20believe%20they%20have%20the%20answer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20a%20team%20of%20scientists%20nearly%20three%20years%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20caused%20a%20mass%20die-off%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-390-botswana-elephants-found-inexplicably-dead-near-water-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eelephants%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Zimbabwe%2C%20but%20they%20finally%20closed%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20August%20and%20September%202020%2C%2035%20elephant%20carcasses%20were%20retrieved%20from%20various%20safaris%20and%20protected%20lands%20in%20Zimbabwe%20%E2%80%94%20with%20eleven%20of%20these%20animals%20dying%20within%20a%2024-hour%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20responsible%20for%20figuring%20out%20what%20happened%20initially%20ruled%20out%20intentional%20poisoning%2C%20poaching%2C%20and%20drought%20conditions%2C%20per%20the%20study%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D8f1d89bb567873c81608109dae97a0c9cf6673815b4059f27e0b1554351c5d39%26postID%3D65499271fe456b34e607d06e%26postSlug%3Dscientists-solve-mystery-of-35-dead-elephants-2023-11%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nature.com%252Farticles%252Fs41467-023-41987-z%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ENature%20Communications%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20didn't%20seem%20to%20be%20any%20signs%20of%20external%20trauma%20on%20the%20elephants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20then%20decided%20to%20look%20inside%20and%20sample%20the%20brain%2C%20liver%2C%20and%20spleen%20tissue%20from%2015%20elephants%20and%20confirmed%20that%20six%20elephants%20had%20bacteria%20known%20as%20Bisgaard%20taxon%2045%20in%20their%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20concluded%20that%20most%2C%20if%20not%20all%2C%20the%20elephants%20died%20as%20a%20result%20of%20septicemia%2C%20or%20blood%20poisoning%2C%20caused%20by%20the%20bacteria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20there%20was%20not%20culture%20or%20molecular%20evidence%20to%20confirm%20Bisgaard%20taxon%2045%20in%20more%20than%20six%20mortalities%20in%20Zimbabwe%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20study%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20elephants%20examined%20were%20in%20good%20body%20condition%20and%20unlikely%20to%20have%20died%20of%20drought-related%20starvation%20or%20severe%20dehydration%20alone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bacteria%20is%20not%20known%20to%20kill%20African%20elephants%2C%20scientists%20said%2C%20but%20they%20are%20beginning%20to%20see%20a%20potential%20pattern%20of%20cases%20like%20this%20in%20herds%20across%20Africa.%20There%20have%20also%20been%20cases%20of%20blood%20infections%20killing%20off%20elephant%20populations%20in%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20authors%20said%20they%20are%20still%20stumped%20as%20to%20how%20the%20bacteria%20was%20transmitted%20to%20the%20elephant%20populations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20authors%20write%20that%20climate%20change-induced%20factors%20like%20heat%2C%20drought%2C%20and%20population%20density%20could%20make%20this%20type%20of%20bacteria%20transmission%20more%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20premature%20to%20say%20that%20climate%20change%20has%20influenced%20(this)%20but%20it%20may%20do%20so%20in%20future%20if%20we%20get%20more%20and%20prolonged%20droughts%2C%20or%20the%20rainfall%20patterns%20(change)%20and%20we%20have%20a%20much%20harsher%20dry%20season%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Chris%20Foggin%2C%20one%20of%20the%20study's%20co-authors%20and%20a%20veterinarian%20at%20Victoria%20Falls%20Wildlife%20Trust%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F11%2F06%2Fafrica%2Fafrican-elephant-deaths-zimbabwe-scn%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etold%20CNN.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20think%20that%20if%20that%20is%20the%20case%2C%20then%20we%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20see%20this%20sort%20of%20mortality%20event%20occurring%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2035%20deaths%20in%20Zimbabwe%20also%20coincided%20with%20a%20mass%20die-off%20of%20elephants%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbotswana-stalling-on-investigation-into-mass-elephant-death-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBotswana%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202020.%20At%20least%20350%20elephants%20died%20within%20a%20three-month%20timespan%2C%20and%20researchers%20at%20the%20time%20concluded%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmass-elephant-die-off-bostwana-toxic-algae-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eblue-green%20algae%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20contaminated%20local%20water%20sources%20and%20poisoned%20the%20elephants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFoggin%20told%20CNN%20that%20the%20scientists%20did%20not%20believe%20the%20deaths%20in%20Botswana%20and%20Zimbabwe%20were%20connected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscientists-solve-mystery-of-35-dead-elephants-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699330967000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65499430b788914e55515694%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscientists-solve-mystery-of-35-dead-elephants-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202020%2C%2035%20elephants%20dropped%20dead%20in%20Zimbabwe%20over%20a%20month%20timespan.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hgetahun%40insider.com%20(Hannah%20Getahun)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscientists-solve-mystery-of-35-dead-elephants-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rishi%20Sunak%20makes%20pre-election%20pitch%20in%20first%20King's%20Speech%20since%201951%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699330929000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105027839%2Cimgsize-53684.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Frishi-sunak-makes-pre-election-pitch-in-first-kings-speech-since-1951%2Farticleshow%2F105027795.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%2