ttisgarh%20and%20Mizoram%20going%20to%20polls%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20state%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMizoram%20will%20see%20polling%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-a-land-of-settled-grief%5C%22%3Ecommunal%20Meitei-Kuki-Zo%20conflict%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20which%20could%20be%20sensed%20even%20among%20the%20Mizo%20people%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20closely%20related%20to%20the%20Kuki%20tribe.%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%2020%20seats%20going%20to%20polls%20are%20in%20the%20Adivasi-dominated%20Bastar%2C%20also%20one%20of%20the%20poorest%20regions%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20regions%20which%20go%20to%20polls%20first%20reflect%20the%20predominance%20of%20issues%20related%20to%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20marginalised%20communities.%20And%20thus%2C%20these%20issues%20are%20foregrounded%20like%20never%20before.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPolitical%20parties%20in%20the%20fray%2C%20across%20all%20the%20five%20states%2C%20have%20centred%20their%20canvassing%20around%20issues%20that%20directly%20impact%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20those%20on%20the%20margins%20of%20the%20Indian%20socio-economic%20make%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkarnataka-election-results-issues-questions%5C%22%3EKarnataka%20assembly%20elections%20showed%20how%20the%20poor%20could%20swing%20the%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20upstage%20a%20state%20government.%20They%20consolidated%20behind%20the%20Congress%20to%20drive%20out%20what%20they%20believed%20was%20a%20corrupt%20and%20anti-poor%20administration.%20Frequent%20complaints%20like%20back-breaking%20price%20rise%2C%20especially%20the%20hike%20in%20LPG%20cylinder%E2%80%99s%20prices%2C%20poorly-managed%20social%20welfare%20programmes%2C%20a%20weakening%20public%20distribution%20system%20in%20the%20state%20could%20be%20heard%20across%20the%20state%20among%20sections%20of%20the%20rural%20poor.%20These%2C%20combined%20with%20perceptible%20investment%20in%20development%20work%20that%20benefited%20only%20the%20big%20businesses%2C%20were%20believed%20to%20be%20primary%20factors%20behind%20the%20impoverishment%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20rural%20population.%20A%20series%20of%20corruption%20scandals%20that%20made%20news%20quite%20frequently%20topped%20up%20as%20further%20insults%20to%20injuries%20of%20a%20majority%20of%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20incumbent%20BJP%20government%20had%20to%20pay%20the%20price%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20which%20emerged%20as%20the%20biggest%20opposition%20force%20registered%20almost%20an%20absolute%20majority%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20mopping%20off%20even%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular).%20This%20party%20too%20had%20been%20in%20the%20thick%20of%20amplifying%20the%20political%20narrative%20against%20the%20B.S.%20Bommai-led%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20year%20will%20now%20end%20with%20new%20governments%20in%20five%20different%20states%2C%20the%20results%20will%20once%20again%20reflect%20the%20political%20will%20of%20the%20poor.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20outcome%20will%20be%20deemed%20significant%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20seek%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%20for%20his%20government%20early%20next%20year.%20Various%20surveys%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20assembly%20polls%20do%20not%20necessarily%20reflect%20the%20mood%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20which%20will%20come%20into%20play%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20However%2C%20since%20the%20assembly%20results%20will%20also%20sharpen%20the%20evolving%2C%20but%20glaring%2C%20ideological%20differences%20between%20the%20saffron%20camp%20and%20the%20opposition%20forces%2C%20they%20will%20likely%20have%20a%20much%20bigger%20impact%20on%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20than%20what%20is%20being%20imagined%20by%20commentators%20currently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20emerging%20political%20binary%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20symbolic%20force%20behind%20large-scale%20infrastructure%20development%20and%20Hindutva-driven%20cultural%20renaissance%20in%20India.%20All%20the%20decisions%20taken%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20poor%20%E2%80%93%20like%20Ujjwala%20LPG%20scheme%2C%20PM%20Awas%20Yojana%2C%20or%20even%20the%20Gareeb%20Kalyan%20Yojana%20which%20provides%20free%20ration%20%E2%80%93%20pale%20in%20front%20of%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20big%20infrastructure%20work.%20Of%20course%2C%20these%20schemes%20have%20done%20wonders%20for%20the%20BJP%20electorally%20in%20the%20short-term%20but%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20draw%20among%20his%20supporters%20is%20that%20of%20a%20futuristic%2C%20visionary%20leader%20who%20can%20help%20India%20become%20a%20developed%20nation%20by%202047.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20big%20infrastructure%20development%20is%20Brand%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20USP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07091746%2FScreenshot-2023-11-07-at-9.14.17.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07091746%2FScreenshot-2023-11-07-at-9.14.17.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07091746%2FScreenshot-2023-11-07-at-9.14.17-300x164.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fupl