20promised%20similar%20schemes%20like%20unemployment%20allowance%2C%20better%20wage%20rates%2C%20education%20and%20health%20infrastructure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20stories%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20are%20also%20similar.%20Congress%20has%20led%20an%20aggressive%20campaign%20by%20promising%20several%20benefits%20to%20the%20poor%2C%20and%20has%20attempted%20to%20gain%20traction%20by%20amplifying%20the%20prevailing%20anti-incumbency%20sentiment%20against%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20and%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20K.%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao-led%20state%20governments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21124421%2FF5gePirW4AAqwSk.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21124421%2FF5gePirW4AAqwSk.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21124421%2FF5gePirW4AAqwSk-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21124421%2FF5gePirW4AAqwSk-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681147%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESingh%20Deo%20with%20Chhattisgarh%20CM%20Bhupesh%20Baghel.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40TS_SinghDeo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20all%20these%20four%20states%2C%20agrarian%20issues%20have%20emerged%20as%20the%20biggest%20grievance%20among%20the%20electorate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20There%20could%20be%20poor%20rates%20for%20the%20crop%2C%20drought-related%20complaints%2C%20water%20crisis%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20insufficient%20planned%20irrigation%2C%20high%20electricity%20prices%2C%