r.com%2Fwework-co-founder-adam-neumann-is-stepping-down-as-ceo-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresigned%20as%20chief%20executive%20in%202019%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eciting%20intense%20public%20scrutiny%20that%20had%20become%20a%20distraction%20in%20running%20the%20firm%20%E2%80%94%20said%20that%20he%20found%20news%20about%20the%20impending%20bankruptcy%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20be%20%26quot%3Bdisappointing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20challenging%20for%20me%20to%20watch%20from%20the%20sidelines%20since%202019%20as%20WeWork%20has%20failed%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20a%20product%20that%20is%20more%20relevant%20today%20than%20ever%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesswire.com%2Fnews%2Fhome%2F20231106843900%2Fen%2FStatement-From-WeWork-Co-Founder-Adam-Neumann%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIt%2520has%2520been%2520challenging%2520for%2Cenable%2520WeWork%2520to%2520emerge%2520successfully%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%2C%20with%20the%20right%20strategy%20and%20team%2C%20a%20reorganization%20will%20enable%20WeWork%20to%20emerge%20successfully.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20its%20peak%2C%20the%20company%20was%20valued%20at%20%2447%20billion%20as%20a%20private%20company.%20But%20the%20startup%20has%20been%20in%20turmoil%20ever%20since%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweworks-nightmare-ipo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplans%20to%20go%20public%20in%202019%20fell%20apart%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20concerns%20about%20the%20company's%20profitability%20and%20some%20of%20Neumann's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femployees-inside-adam-neumanns-wework-reveal-a-wild-culture-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einappropriate%20antics%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapanese%20investor%20SoftBank%20has%20dropped%20billions%20of%20dollars%20into%20the%20real%20estate%20st