elp%20underpin%20AI%20systems.%20Accenture's%20bargaining%20unit%20asked%20for%20more%20control%20over%20which%20Google%20assignments%20they%20had%20to%20accept%2C%20if%20it%20was%20outside%20the%20scope%20of%20their%20usual%20work%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0including%20their%20work%20on%20Bard.%20Organizers%20also%20sought%20better%20pay%2C%20benefits%2C%20and%20paid%20time%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%2080%20Accenture%20workers%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.engadget.com%2Fgoogle-contract-workers-accuse-alphabet-and-accenture-of-violating-labor-laws-085100869.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elaid%20off%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20fledgling%20union%20filed%20a%20complaint%20to%20the%20National%20Labor%20Relations%20Board%20shortly%20after%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20layoffs%20were%20retaliatory%20and%20therefore%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20organized%20so%20that%20we%20could%20have%20a%20say%20in%20our%20working%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20Jen%20Hill%2C%20a%20Google%20Help%20Designer%20and%20member%20of%20the%20Alphabet%20Workers%20Union%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BIn%20response%2C%20Google%20has%20tried%20to%20skirt%20its%20responsibility%20to%20us%20as%20our%20employer%2C%20while%20also%20laying%20off%20dozens%20of%20our%20team%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20is%20currently%20appealing%20the%20NLRB's%20September%20ruling%20that%20it%20is%20joint%20employer%20of%20Accenture%20contractors.%20If%20successful%2C%20the%20appeal%20could%20shield%20Google%20from%20legal%20liability%20after%20laying%20off%20the%20organizing%20Accenture%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20spokesperson%20Courtenay%20Mencini%20said%20the%20company%20has%20no%20objection%20to%20Accenture%20workers%20unionizing%20and%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bas%20we%20made%20clear%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nlrb.gov%2Fcase%2F20-RC-319743%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eactive%20appeal%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20NLRB%2C%20we%20are%20not%20a%20joint%20employer%20as%20we%20simply%20do%20not%20control%20their%20employment%20terms%20or%20working%20conditions%20%E2%80%93%20this%20matter%20is%20between%20the%20workers%20and%20their%20employer%2C%20Accenture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NLRB%20declined%20to%20comment.%20An%20Accenture%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20the%20company%20will%20continue%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20NLRB%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20acknowledge%20the%20right%20of%20our%20people%20to%20form%20or%20join%20unions%2C%20and%20we%20work%20cooperatively%20with%20works%20councils%20and%20labor%20unions%20in%20various%20countries%20around%20the%20globe%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAccenture%20contractors%20worked%20on%20Bard%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20rushed%20its%20release%20of%20Bard%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-bard-launch-europe-brazil-new-features-languages-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emake%20a%20product%20to%20compete%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT.%20Many%20Accenture%20workers%20were%20recruited%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Btop%20secret%20project%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20ended%20up%20being%20work%20on%20Bard%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20230608131411%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-06-08%2Fgoogle-contract-staff-that-helped-train-ai-seek-to-unionize%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBloomberg%20reported%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January.%20Workers%20said%20they%20had%20to%20fact-check%20the%20large%20language%20model's%20prompt%20responses%20and%20engineer%20their%20own%20answers%20to%20theoretical%20prompts.%20These%20prompts%20included%20%26quot%3Bobscene%2C%20graphic%20and%20offensive%26quot%3B%20content%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20230608131411%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%