The%20straight-A%20student%20said%20it's%20a%20misconception%20that%20working%20with%20buses%20is%20a%20dead-end%20job.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EOur%20desire%20for%20paper%20qualifications%20can%20blind%20us%20to%20real%20opportunities%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%4099colours%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMatthew%20Tay%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20an%20operations%20supervisor%20in%20Singapore%20for%20Tower%20Transit%2C%20a%20local%20bus%20company.%20This%20essay%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Insider%20verified%20his%20educational%20background%2C%20college%20acceptance%20letters%2C%20and%20employment%20details.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20in%20Hougang%2C%20a%20neighborhood%20in%20northeast%20Singapore%2C%20near%20a%20now%20defunct%20bus%20interchange.%20When%20I%20was%20a%20kid%2C%20my%20parents%20took%20me%20around%20a%20lot%20to%20different%20bus%20interchanges%2C%20and%20it%20sparked%20my%20interest%20in%20collecting%20brochures%20about%20buses%20and%20drawing%20the%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20older%2C%20I%20joined%20a%20400-member%20Facebook%20group%20called%20%26quot%3BSingapore%20bus%20enthusiasts.%26quot%3B%20I%20remember%20being%20the%20youngest%20person%20in%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20then%2C%20buses%20were%20like%20Pok%C3%A9mon%20%E2%80%94%20you%20could%20catch%20only%20certain%20types%20of%20vehicles%20depending%20on%20which%20part%20of%20Singapore%20you%20were%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20weekend%2C%20the%20group%20would%20target%20places%20to%20go%20to%20hop%20onto%20some%20of%20these%20buses.%20Like%20in%202012%2C%20the%20last%20non-air-conditioned%20buses%20were%20found%20only%20in%20the%20far-west%20industrial%20areas%20of%20Tuas%20%E2%80%94%20a%20neighborhood%20in%20western%20Singapore%20%E2%80%94%20so%20the%20group%20headed%20there%20to%20experience%20what%20it%20was%20like%20to%20ride%20on%20a%20bus%20with%20no%20air%20conditioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20just%20tag%20along%20for%20bus-spotting%20trips%20but%20also%20collected%20memorabilia%20as%20I%20grew%20older.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20collecting%20bus%20models%20from%20across%20the%20world%20when%20I%20was%2012%2C%20and%20I%20now%20have%20over%2030%20models%20in%20my%20collection%2C%20each%20costing%20about%2070%20Singapore%20dollars%2C%20or%20about%20%2450.%20I%20think%20I've%20spent%20about%202%2C000%20Singapore%20dollars%20on%20them%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20I've%20also%20collected%20bus%20memorabilia%20such%20as%20seats%2C%20a%20giant%20bus%20electronic%20display%2C%20and%20even%20a%20bus%20dashboard.%20I%20salvaged%20many%20of%20these%20items%20by%20buying%20them%20from%20scrapyard%20workers%20and%20then%20restoring%20them.%20I%20think%20I've%20spent%20thousands%20of%20Singapore%C2%A0dollars%20on%20these%2C%20but%20I%20haven't%20kept%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Matthew%20Tay%20and%20his%20collection%20of%20bus%20memorabilia%2C%20which%20includes%20his%20bus%20models%2C%20salvaged%20bus%20number%20plates%2C%20and%20a%20bus%20electronic%20display%20he%20restored.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65388c3a96f7540cd064c528%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMatthew%20Tay%20and%20his%20collection%20of%20bus%20memorabilia%2C%20which%20includes%20his%20bus%20models%2C%20salvaged%20bus%20number%20plates%2C%20and%20a%20bus%20electronic%20display%20he%20restored.%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Tay%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20was%20a%20top-scoring%20student%2C%20and%20people%20expected%20me%20to%20go%20to%20college.%20But%20I%20didn't.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20time%20in%20national%20service%20%E2%80%94%20Singapore's%20military%20conscription%20for%20male%20citizens%20%E2%80%94%20I%20picked%20up%20bus%20driving%20on%20the%20weekends%2C%20volunteering%20with%20a%20company.%20That's%20how%20I%20got%20the%20license%20to%20drive%20a%20bus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20experience%20further%20fueled%20my%20passion%20for%20buses%20and%20made%20me%20realize%20that%20I%20shouldn't%20go%20to%20college%20%E2%80%94%20I%20should%20start%20looking%20for%20jobs%20in%20the%20bus%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20when%20I%20applied%20to%20Tower%20Transit%20Singapore%2C%20a%20local%20bus%20company%20that%20operates%2059%20bus%20services%20out%20of%20nine%20interchanges%20in%20Singapore%20where%20I%20now%20work%20as%20an%20operations%20supervisor.%20I%20joined%20the%20team%20in%20August%202022%2C%20and%20I%20help%20keep%20our%20facilities%20working%20and%20our%20buses%20on%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20it%20has%20been%20a%20dream%20job%20for%20me%2C%20my%20decision%20to%20skip%20college%20was%20shocking%20to%20some.%20That's%20because%20I%20was%20accepted%20into%20Singapore's%20top%20three%20universities%20%E2%80%94%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%2C%20the%20Nanyang%20Technological%20University%2C%20and%20the%20Singapore%20Management%20University%20%E2%80%94%20to%20get%20a%20bachelor's%20degree%20in%20business%2C%20information%20systems%2C%20or%20public%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20classmates%20were%20surprised%20%E2%80%94%20they%20all%20expected%20me%20to%20attend%20college%20because%20of%20how%20well%20I%20scored.%20I%20was%20a%20straight-A%20student%2C%20and%20my%20GPA%20in%20polytechnic%2C%20or%20Singapore's%20equivalent%20to%20a%20vocational%20high%20school%2C%20was%20a%20nearly%20perfect%203.99%20out%20of%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20lecturers%20found%20out%2C%20they%20even%20messaged%20me%20saying%20a%20university%20degree%20was%20something%20I%20should%20seriously%20consider%20in