%20the%20crisis%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20a%20long-term%20rivalry%20with%20China%2C%20which%20%26quot%3Binvolves%20something%20of%20an%20economic%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20Walt%20said%2C%20as%20well%20as%20military%20posturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20I%20think%20the%20only%20thing%20that's%20going%20to%20shift%20the%20attention%20back%20to%20Ukraine%20would%20be%20some%20really%20substantial%20setback%2C%20and%20nobody%20wishes%20that%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Walt%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20it%20looks%20like%20Russia%20is%20about%20to%20make%20substantial%20gains%20again%2C%20that%20could%20get%20the%20problem%20in%20Ukraine%20back%20on%20the%20front%20pages.%20And%20it%20then%20puts%20the%20Biden%20administration%20in%20a%20terrible%20position%20where%20they%20have%20to%20decide%3A%20are%20they%20going%20to%20do%20more%20to%20prevent%20a%20decisive%20Russian%20victory%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-gaza-hamas-war-benefit-putin-russia-ukraine-invasion-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699315444000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6548527f36d588dc55cb2bb1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-gaza-hamas-war-benefit-putin-russia-ukraine-invasion-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Zelenskyy%20is%20right%20that%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20is%20distracting%20the%20world%20from%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%2C%20experts%20say%2C%20splitting%20US%20military%20aid%20priorities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40insider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-gaza-hamas-war-benefit-putin-russia-ukraine-invasion-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Justine%20Blainey%3A%2