2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20letters%20got%20%26quot%3Bagonizingly%20close%26quot%3B%20to%20reaching%20the%20soldiers%2C%20before%20being%20seized%20by%20officials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20steamy%20letter%20sent%20more%20than%20two%20centuries%20ago%2C%20Anne%20Le%20Cerf%20wrote%20to%20her%20husband%2C%20an%20imprisoned%20French%20naval%20officer%2C%20that%20she%20could%20not%20%26quot%3Bwait%20to%20possess%26quot%3B%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20embrace%20you%20with%20my%20heart%2C%20being%20unable%20to%20do%20it%20with%20my%20lips%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20another%20wife%20to%20her%20husband%2C%20Jean%20Baptiste%20Emmanuel%20Gilbert%2C%20a%20master%20calker%20on%20the%20Galat%C3%A9e%2C%20a%20captured%20French%20warship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20fatigued%20and%20impatient%20of%20not%20being%20able%20to%20enjoy%20your%20amiable%20presence.%20I%20can%20assure%20you%20that%20days%20seem%20like%20months%2C%20and%20months%20like%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20another%20letter%2C%20translated%20to%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20loving%20words%20never%20reached%20their%20intended%20destination.%20For%20more%20than%20265%20years%2C%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F11-greatest-presidential-love-letters-2012-2%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eletters%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20along%20with%20more%20than%20100%20others%20sent%20to%20French%20prisoners%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20were%20left%20unread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fap-world-war-ii-vet-reunited-with-love-letter-72-years-later-2017-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eletters%3C%2Fa%3E%20contain%20intimate%20messages%20from%20the%20fianc%C3%A9es%20and%20wives%20of%20French%20sailors%20imprisoned%20during%20the%20Seven%20Years'%20War%20between%201756%20and%201763.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20seized%20by%20British%20officials%2C%20they%20lay%20untouched%20in%20the%20National%20Archives%20in%20Kew%2C%20London%2C%20before%20Renaud%20Morieux%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20history%20from%20Cambridge%20University%2C%20decided%20to%20open%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223336%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20ancient%20letter%2C%20creased%20where%20it%20used%20to%20be%20folded%2C%20is%20laid%20out%20flat%20on%20a%20table.%20Writing%20is%20seen%20on%20the%20insider%20of%20the%20letter%20covering%20most%20of%20the%20paper.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6548c57836d588dc55cb3a04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20picture%20shows%20one%20of%20the%20long-lost%20letters%20addressed%20to%20french%20sailors%20over%20265%20years%20ago.%20This%20letter%2C%20addressed%20by%20Anne%20Le%20Cerf%20to%20her%20husband%2C%20reads%20%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20wait%20to%20possess%20you.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Archives%20%2F%20Renaud%20Morieux%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20spend%20the%20night%20writing%20to%20you...I%20am%20your%20forever%20faithful%20wife.%20Good%20night%2C%20my%20dear%20friend.%20It%20is%20midnight.%20I%20think%20it%20is%20time%20for%20me%20to%20rest%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20one%20letter%20by%20Marie%20Dubosc%20to%20her%20husband%2C%20a%20Lieutenant%20on%20the%20Galat%C3%A9e.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eurekalert.org%2Fnews-releases%2F1006737%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMorieux's%20investigation%3C%2Fa%3E%20revealed%20that%20Dubosc%20died%20a%20year%20after%20sending%20her%20letter.%20Her%20husband%20never%20read%20her%20message%20and%20remarried%20shortly%20after%20being%20released%20from%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Seven%20Years'%20War%20was%20a%20conflict%20between%20France%20and%20Britain%20that%20began%20as%20a%20dispute%20over%20North%20American%20land.%20It%20spread%20into%20conflict%20in%20other%20parts%20of%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Europe%2C%20North%20America%2C%20Africa%2C%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%2020%2C000%20French%20sailors%20were%20captured%20by%20the%20British%20military%20to%20thwart%20France's%20effort%20to%20crew%20their%20state-of-the-art%20ships%20during%20the%20Seven%20Year%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20war%3Cspan%3E%2C%20France%20commanded%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20advanced%20ships%20but%20lacked%20experienced%20sailors.%20To%20take%20advantage%20of%20this%2C%20Britain%20imprisoned%20as%20many%20French%20sailors%20as%20it%20could%20throughout%20the%20war.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201758%2C%20out%20of%2060%2C137%20French%20sailors%2C%20a%20third%20were%20detained%20in%20Britain%2C%20according%20to%20the%20press%20release.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELetters%20to%20the%20French%20prisoners%20were%20redirected%20to%20England%20when%20the%20ships%20were%20captured.%20Morieux%20believes%20they%20got%20%26quot%3Bagonizingly%20close%26quot%3B%20to%20reaching%20their%20destination%2C%20but%20English%20officials%20opened%20only%20two%2C%20decided%20they%20likely%20had%20no%20military%20value%2C%20and%20stored%20them%20rather%20than%20pass%20on%20potentially%20sensitive%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20realized%20I%20was%20the%20first%20person%20to%20read%20these%20very%20personal%20messages%20since%20they%20were%20written.%20Their%20intended%20recipients%20didn't%20get%20that%20chance.%20It%20was%20very%20emotional%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20letters%20are%20more%20than%20two%20centuries%20old%2C%20the%20sentiments%20shared%20by%20the%20women%2C%20who%20authored%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20letters%2C%20are%20remarkably%20familiar%2C%20Morieux%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20are%20separated%20from%20loved%20ones%20by%20events%20beyond%20our%20control%20like%20the%20pandemic%20or%20wars%2C%20we%20have%20to%20work%20out%20how%20to%20stay%20in%20touch%2C%20how%20to%20reassure%2C%20care%20for%20people%2C%20and%20keep%20the%20passion%20alive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20difference%20is%20that%20these%20messages%20were%2C%20to%20some%20extent%2C%20more%20public%20than%20messages%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaper%20was%20expensive%2C%20so%20love%20messages%20were%20often%20tagged%20onto%20the%20bottom%20of%20letters%20written%20by%20other%20family%20members.%20Many%20of%20these%20women%20were%20illiterate%20and%20would%20have%20required%20someone%20else%20to%20write%20their%20love%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20people%20sending%20these%20letters%20were%20telling%20a%20scribe%20what%20they%20wanted%20to%20say%2C%20and%20relied%20on%20others%20to%20read%20their%20letters%20aloud.%20This%20was%20someone%20they%20knew%20who%20could%20write%2C%20not%20a%20professional.%20Staying%20in%20touch%20was%20a%20community%20effort%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Morieux.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letters%20and%20their%20analysis%20were%20published%20in%20the%20French%20journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fdx.doi.org%2F10.1017%2Fahss.2023.75%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BAnnales%2C%20Histoire%2C%20Sciences%20Sociales%26quot%3B%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteamy-letters-love-french-sailors-opened-first-time-265-years-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699315261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6548c6a63cc84b4dfafcd02e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteamy-letters-love-french-sailors-opened-first-time-265-years-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20of%20the%20letters%20contain%20intimate%20messages%20from%20the%20fianc%C3%A9es%20and%20wives%20of%20French%20sailors%20imprisoned%20during%20the%20Seven%20Years'%20War%20between%20175