r%20bodies%20and%20know%20what%E2%80%99s%20normal%20for%20them%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20something%20seems%20different%2C%20especially%20with%20serious%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290057%2Fchhavi-mittal-breast-cancer-actress-awareness%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econditions%20like%20cancer%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20consult%20a%20doctor.%20I%20was%20fortunate%20to%20catch%20mine%20early!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699280733000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333669%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Diagnosed%20with%20Acute%20Lymphoblastic%20Leukemia%2C%20Meher%20Roy%20thanks%20his%20father%20for%20instilling%20a%20habit%20of%20checking%20up%20his%20heart%2C%20kidneys%2C%20and%20lungs%20regularly.%20It%20was%20on%20one%20of%20these%20regular%20health%20tests%20that%20he%20was%20able%20to%20detect%20cancer%20at%20an%20early%20stage%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20timely%20action.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Busting%20Myths%2C%20Maharashtra%20Couple%20Saves%20Over%206000%20Snake%20Bite%20Victims%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELast%20August%2C%20Pune%E2%80%99s%20Ramprakash%20Kharge%20woke%20up%20with%20a%20strange%20pain%20in%20his%20leg.%20When%20he%20looked%20at%20the%20site%20of%20pain%2C%20he%20found%20it%20swollen.%20The%2064-year-old%20farmer%20wondered%20if%20he%20had%20slipped%20in%20the%20field%20to%20lead%20to%20this.%20Not%20paying%20much%20mind%20to%20it%2C%20he%20went%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20he%20observed%20that%20the%20skin%20around%20the%20bite%20discoloured.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20turned%20bluish%20and%20blackish%20and%20people%20suspected%20it%20could%20be%20due%20to%20a%20snakebite%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20son%20Kiran%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20rushed%20to%20Vighnahar%20Nursing%20Clinic%20in%20Narayangaon%20where%20the%20farmer%20was%20kept%20under%20observation%20for%20three%20days.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20on%20ventilation.%20The%20doctor%20suspected%20that%20he%20might%20be%20bitten%20by%20a%20Russell%E2%80%99s%20viper%20%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20the%20most%20venomous%20snakes.%20We%20were%20so%20scared%20as%20this%20was%20the%20first%20such%20case%20in%20our%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20feared%20that%20the%20venom%20might%20have%20spread%20to%20the%20kidneys%20and%20heart.%20The%20doctor%20had%20performed%20a%20surgery%20to%20remove%20the%20toxins.%20Each%20moment%20was%20difficult%20for%20us.%20But%20the%20surgery%20was%20successful%20and%20my%20father%20was%20safe%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%20with%20a%20sigh%20of%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%202022%20study%20estimates%20that%20India%20reports%20at%20least%2064%2C000%20snakebite%20deaths%20every%20year%2C%20especially%20making%20people%20living%20in%20the%20rural%20hinterlands%20more%20vulnerable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-2-1699278240.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Sadanand%20says%20that%20they%20get%20at%20least%20200%20snakebite%20cases%20every%20year.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-2-1699278240.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-2-1699278240-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-2-1699278240-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.theb