f%20almost%2010%20hours%20in%20case%20of%20a%20power%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20bulb%20that%20solves%20the%20problem.%20Speaking%20to%20those%20young%20children%20and%20seeing%20their%20troubles%20really%20moved%20me.%20Reading%20about%20the%20heat%20crisis%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20motivated%20me%20to%20solve%20this%20problem.%20How%20could%20they%20stay%20without%20electricity%20in%20such%20extreme%20weather%20conditions%3F%E2%80%9D%20Uday%20Bhatia%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20solution%20at%20Rs%20250%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20768px)%20100vw%2C%20768px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday2-2-1699023289.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Uday%20worked%20on%2024%20prototypes%20over%208%20months%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday2-2-1699023289.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday2-2-1699023289-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday2-2-1699023289-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday2-2-1699023289-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday2-2-1699023289-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333623%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EUday%20worked%20on%2024%20prototypes%20over%208%20months.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20hard%20to%20find%20a%20solution%2C%20Uday%20first%20realised%20that%20there%20was%20no%20cost-effective%20solution%20for%20the%20rural%20population.%20He%20says%20that%20his%20first%20thought%20was%20to%20build%20something%20using%20renewable%20energy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20going%20through%20many%20ideas%2C%20I%20conceptualised%20a%20bulb%20that%20has%20the%20capabilities%20of%20an%20inverter%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20power%20outage.%20I%20designed%20it%20specifically%20for%20remote%20villages%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%20in%20April%202022%2C%20the%20Class%2012%20student%20who%20is%20passionate%20about%20computer%20science%2C%20set%20up%20a%20workstation%20on%20his%20terrace%20with%20a%20soldering%20iron%20and%20a%20couple%20of%20wires%2C%20beginning%20his%20experiments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20how%20to%20assemble%20a%20bulb%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333159%2Fdelhi-startup-dhananjaya-bharadwaj-abhimanyu-singh-parkmate-find-parking-app%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epulse%20modulation%20algorithm%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20watching%20YouTube%20videos%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20he%20built%20a%20bulb%20with%20a%20four-hour%20backup.%20But%20he%20wanted%20to%20provide%20an%208-10%20hour%20backup%2C%20which%20he%20was%20able%20to%20do%20thanks%20to%20computer%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20use%20a%20lithium%20ion%20battery%2C%20which%20has%20a%20backup%20of%20four%20hours.%20Now%2C%20I%20had%20to%20increase%20the%20backup%20time%2C%20without%20increasing%20the%20size%20of%20the%20cell.%20I%20applied%20the%20concept%20of%20control%20systems%20to%20increase%20the%20backup%20time.%20I%20did%20various%20trials%20using%20the%20pulse%20width%20modulation%20algorithm%20to%20achieve%20the%20desired%20result.%20This%20algorithm%20helped%20me%20optimise%20energy%20consumption%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20algorithm%20further%2C%20he%20says%20that%20he%20developed%20a%20way%20to%20adjust%20the%20bulb%E2%80%99s%20brightness%2C%20which%20extends%20the%20time%20of%20backup.%20If%20you%20lower%20the%20brightness%2C%20you%20get%20a%20longer%20backup.%20The%20bulb%20comes%20with%20settings%20to%20change%20the%20brightness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20bulb%20works%2C%20Uday%20states%20that%20the%20technology%20used%20is%20very%20simple.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20bulb%20is%20connected%20to%20a%20power%20source%2C%20energy%20gets%20stored%20in%20the%20battery.%20When%20the%20power%20supply%20is%20cut%20off%2C%20the%20bulb%20uses%20the%20energy%20stored%20in%20the%20battery%20to%20glow.%20I%20have%20done%20this%20using%20a%20rectifier%2C%20to%20make%20it%20glow%20during%20a%20power%20outage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIlluminating%20over%207%2C000%20households%20in%205%20states%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20768px)%20100vw%2C%20768px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday3-2-1699023290.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Uday%20has%20sold%20over%207000%20bulbs%20so%20far%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday3-2-1699023290.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday3-2-1699023290-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday3-2-1699023290-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday3-2-1699023290-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday3-2-1699023290-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333624%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EUday%20has%20sold%20over%207%2C000%20bulbs%20so%20far.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20selling%20this%20through%20his%20venture%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304454%2Ftwo-friends-climate-tech-startup-climes-helps-neutralise-carbon-footprint%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%98Uday%20Electric%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Rs%20250%20a%20piece%20from%20May%202022.%20The%20bulbs%20come%20with%20a%201%20year%20warranty.%20The%20tagline%20of%20the%20company%20is%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBijli%20gul%20phir%20bhi%20ujjala%20full%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(Even%20with%20the%20power%20cut%2C%20there%20will%20still%20be%20light).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20bootstrapped%20the%20venture%20with%20Rs%2030%2C000%2C%20which%20he%20used%20to%20buy%20the%20table%20and%20supplies%20needed%20for%2050%20bulbs.%20For%20the%20sales%2C%20he%20initially%20started%20visiting%20a%20few%20markets%20and%20doing%20the%20sales%20himself.%20Since%20that%20was%20not%20feasible%20in%20all%20areas%2C%20he%20worked%20with%20local%20farmers%20and%20villagers%20to%20sell%20his%20bulb.%20This%20also%20provides%20them%20with%20an%20extra%20income.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20so%20far%20sold%20over%207%2C000%20units%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20to%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Delhi.%20Of%20these%2C%20950%20units%20were%20donated%20to%20households%20in%20the%20Kabadi%20Bazar%2C%20Dehradun%2C%20through%20Aasra%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20particular%20area%20had%20no%20electricity%20for%20most%20part%20of%20the%20day.%20When%20I%20saw%20the%20joy%20on%20people%E2%80%99s%20faces%20when%20their%20houses%20were%20illuminated%2C%20I%20felt%20on%20top%20of%20the%20world.%20No%20feeling%20can%20come%20close%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20the%2018-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmit%20Balodi%20of%20Aasra%20Foundation%20says%20that%20many%20in%20the%20slums%20of%20Kabadi%20Bazaar%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20access%20to%20electricity%20and%20these%20bulbs%20have%20been%20of%20great%20help%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20these%20labourers%20live%20in%20slums%20and%20these%20bulbs%20have%20been%20very%20useful%20to%20them%20at%20night.%20They%20charge%20them%20during%20the%20day%20and%20use%20them%20at%20night.%20It%20greatly%20helps%20in%20energy%20conservation%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Amit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUday%20won%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322755%2Fkarnataka-divaa-uthkarsha-project-surya-type-one-diabetes-awareness-for-underprivileged-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDiana%20Award%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20set%20up%20in%20memory%20of%20the%20late%20Princess%20of%20Wales%2C%20and%20honours%20%E2%80%98outstanding%20young%20people%20selflessly%20creating%20positive%20social%20change%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20making%20the%20bulbs%20on%20his%20terrace%2C%20he%20now%20outsources%20manufacturing.%20He%20wants%20to%20continue%20illuminating%20more%20households%20in%20rural%20areas%20and%20wants%20to%20make%20a%20tubelight%20using%20the%20same%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20make%20a%20tubelight%20that%20will%20help%20factories%20located%20in%20rural%20areas.%20This%20will%20help%20them%20save%20cost%20and%20decrease%20inverter%20usage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUday%20wishes%20to%20bring%20light%20to%20as%20many%20households%20as%20he%20can%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Fenvironment%2Fcrisis-hit-uttarakhand-struck-by-power-shortage-cent