0He%20would%20also%20go%20on%20to%20compete%20in%20the%201952%20Helsinki%20Olympics%2C%20representing%20India%20in%20water%20polo.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20incredible%20achievements%20in%20the%20pool%2C%20he%20would%20train%20future%20generations%20of%20Indian%20swimmers%20%E2%80%94%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F88621%2Farati-saha-first-indian-asian-woman-swim-english-channel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArati%20Saha%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20first%20Asian%20woman%20to%20cross%20the%20English%20channel%20in%201959%2C%20and%20Nafisa%20Ali%2C%20a%20national%20champion%20in%20the%20early%201970s%20who%20was%20also%20crowned%20Miss%20World.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDesire%20for%20recognition%2C%20acknowledgement%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20his%20many%20achievements%20for%20the%20country%20against%20incredible%20odds%2C%20Nag%20passed%20away%20on%2019%20August%2C%201987%2C%20without%20real%20recognition%20or%20financial%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202014%2C%20Ashoke%20Kumar%20Nag%2C%20his%20son%20and%20a%20Kolkata-based%20insurance%20agent%20at%20the%20time%2C%20recalled%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20yearned%20for%20recognition%20from%20the%20government.%20Not%20financial%20considerations%20but%20the%20acknowledgement%20of%20his%20service%20to%20the%20sport%20and%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20Ashoke%20tried%20to%20secure%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20but%20was%20often%20met%20with%20bureaucratic%20apathy%20and%20rejection.%20On%20multiple%20occasions%2C%20he%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Sports%20Ministry%20to%20bestow%20an%20award%20to%20his%20father%20posthumously%20in%20recognition%20of%20his%20achievements%2C%20and%20he%20never%20gave%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202020%2C%20Nag%20was%20awarded%20the%20Dhyan%20Chand%20Award%20for%20lifetime%20achievement%20in%20sports.%20Finally%2C%20one%20of%20post-Independence%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20sporting%20superstars%20received%20the%20recognition%20he%20deserved.%20Ideally%2C%20he%20should%20have%20been%20celebrated%20during%20his%20lifetime%2C%20but%20better%20late%20than%20never.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Pictures%20courtesy%20Wikipedia%20and%20Twitter)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Honour%20for%20pool%20pioneer%E2%80%99%20by%20Arindam%20Bandyopadhyay%3B%20Published%20on%2029%20August%202020%20by%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fsports%2Fhonour-for-pool-pioneer%2Fcid%2F1790335%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Sachin%20Nag%20%E2%80%93%20a%20forgotten%20legend%20by%20Vijay%20Lokapally%E2%80%99%3B%20Published%20on%2029%20September%202014%20by%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fsport%2Fother-sports%2Fsachin-nag-a-forgotten-legend%2Farticle6455156.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98The%20long%20wait%20ends%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20Asiad%20gold%20medallist%20Sachin%20Nag%E2%80%99%20by%20Nihal%20Koshie%3B%20Published%20on%2029%20August%202020%20for%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fthe-long-wait-ends-for-indias-first-asiad-gold-medallist-sachin-nag-6574425%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express