3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etryst%20with%20photography%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20in%20school%20when%20his%20English%20teacher%20loaned%20him%20money%20to%20buy%20a%20camera%2C%20sensing%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20keen%20eye.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESatyan%20and%20the%20camera%20he%20bought%20for%20Rs%20350%20were%20inseparable.%20It%20won%20him%20accolades%20and%20love%20from%20those%20who%20watched%20his%20work.%20An%20interesting%20anecdote%20is%20of%20how%20Satyan%20attempted%20to%20repay%20his%20teacher%20for%20this%20gift%2C%20but%20the%20latter%20instead%20asked%20him%20to%20develop%20a%20picture%20book%20on%20Karnataka.%20Years%20later%20when%20Satyan%20became%20an%20accomplished%20photographer%2C%20he%20returned%20to%20his%20teacher%20with%20the%20said%20book%20that%20even%20featured%20text%20by%20journalist%20and%20writer%20H%20Y%20Sharada%20Prasad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20Satyan%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325308%2Frare-wildlife-conservation-photos-from-across-the-world-nature-infocus-kalyan-varma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforay%20into%20photography%3C%2Fa%3E%20began%20in%20his%20early%20years%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20until%201948%20that%20he%20delved%20into%20it%20professionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20humble%20background%20to%20his%20work%20getting%20recognised%20on%20global%20platforms%2C%20his%20story%20is%20an%20inspiring%20one.%20And%20he%20is%20rightly%20dubbed%20the%20%E2%80%98Father%20of%20Indian%20Photojournalism%E2%80%99.%20We%20take%20a%20look%20at%20his%20incredible%20journey%20and%20the%20moments%20that%20shaped%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20fated%20photographer%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20graduation%20in%20Arts%20from%20Maharaja%E2%80%99s%20College%2C%20Mysuru%2C%20Satyan%20joined%20as%20an%20engine%20inspector%20at%20Hindustan%20Aeronautics.%20He%20then%20worked%20as%20a%20teacher%20at%20a%20school%20followed%20by%20working%20as%20a%20newsreader%20at%20the%20%E2%80%98Akashvani%E2%80%99%20radio%20station.%20All%20this%20time%2C%20he%20remained%20connected%20with%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317185%2Fbollywood-celebrity-photographer-munna-thaakur-recalls-struggle-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20love%20of%20photography%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20in%201948%2C%20when%20a%20vacancy%20opened%20up%20for%20a%20staff%20photographer%20at%20the%20newly%20launched%20Deccan%20Herald%20%E2%80%94%20an%20English%20daily%20based%20in%20Karnataka%20%E2%80%94%20Satyan%20grabbed%20the%20opportunity.%20This%20was%20his%20first%20professional%20stint%20with%20a%20camera%20and%20he%20delivered%20to%20impress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201445px)%20100vw%2C%201445px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Flicensed-image_11zon-1699013197.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221445%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22T%20S%20Satyan%20was%20known%20for%20his%20trademark%20black%20and%20white%20pictures%20that%20captured%20the%20mood%20of%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Flicensed-image_11zon-1699013197.jpg%201445w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Flicensed-image_11zon-1699013197-212x300.jpg%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Flicensed-image_11zon-1699013197-500x709.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Flicensed-image_11zon-1699013197-768x1088.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Flicensed-image_11zon-1699013197-1084x1536.jpg%201084w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Flicensed-image_11zon-1699013197-150x213.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333534%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ET%20S%20Satyan%20was%20known%20for%20his%20trademark%20black%20and%20white%20pictures%20that%20captured%20the%20mood%20of%20India%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Wikipedia%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20trademark%20black-and-white%20pictures%20chronicled%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20mood.%20Satyan%20made%20his%20mark%20as%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20earliest%20photojournalists%20at%20a%20time%20when%20photography%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296104%2Findia-first-selfie-by-maharaja-bir-chandra-of-tripura%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elimited%20to%20portraits%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%20his%20assignment%20in%20the%20Deccan%20Herald%2C%20Satyan%20spent%20the%20next%2060%20years%20documenting%20both%20the%20momentous%20and%20regular%20moments%20in%20Indian%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20certain%20magic%20to%20the%20pictures%20he%20captured%20as%20if%20stealing%20a%20moment%20in%20time%20from%20his%20subject%E2%80%99s%20life.%20As%20he%20once%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20photography%20are%20slices%20of%20human%20life%2C%20gentle%20and%20personal.%20Their%20aim%20is%20to%20let%20the%20viewer%20see%20all%20by%20himself.%20They%20tend%20not%20to%20preach%2C%20not%20to%20pose%20as%20art.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESatyan%20always%20emphasised%20that%20his%20pictures%20were%20not%20the%20result%20of%20encounters%20between%20events%20and%20him%20but%20rather%20a%20witness%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290133%2Fkerala-photographer-sharun-recreates-raja-ravi-varma-paintings-with-trans-models%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einteresting%20moments%20in%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20people%20he%20met.%20%E2%80%9CPhotog