%20camera%20six%20decades%20ago%2C%20and%20they%20have%20been%20there%20every%20time%20I%20have%20gone%20back%20to%20capture%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F262805%2Fdorje-angchuk-ladakh-night-stars-galaxy-sky-pictures%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einteresting%20moments%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20photography%20made%20waves%2C%20his%20words%20did%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESatyan%E2%80%99s%20memoir%20%E2%80%98Alive%20and%20Clicking%E2%80%99%20published%20in%202005%20tells%20the%20story%20of%20the%20days%20he%20spent%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Sikkim%20amongst%20others%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F260630%2Fphoto-journalist-viral-retirement-travel-tokyo-olympics-sachin-tendulkar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrief%20encounters%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20led%20to%20some%20of%20his%20best%20work.%20As%20he%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20spend%20eighty%20summers%20on%20one%20planet%20with%20a%20camera%20in%20hand%2C%20things%20happen%2C%20events%20occur%2C%20and%20you%20have%20a%20bunch%20of%20experiences%20and%20encounters%20because%20you%20were%20there%20at%20the%20right%20time%20at%20the%20right%20place.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESatyan%20passed%20away%20in%202009%20in%20Mysore%20but%20not%20before%20leaving%20behind%20a%20legacy%20of%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20a%20look%20at%20it%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201500px)%20100vw%2C%201500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08_PHY.10165-1_11zon-1699013606.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Flash%20Floods%2C%20Delhi%2C%201970%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fupl