4%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20over%2010%2C000%20drivers%20in%20Bhubaneswar%E2%80%99s%20Smart%20City%20Online%20Auto%20Association.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EDinabandhu%20returned%20to%20his%20home%20in%20Bhubaneswar%20in%202015%20after%20a%20stint%20in%20Hyderabad.%20After%20a%20few%20failed%20businesses%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20start%20driving%20an%20auto%2C%20considering%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfoolproof%20investment%E2%80%9D.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20arrival%20of%20ride-hailing%20apps%20like%20Ola%2C%20Uber%20and%20Rapido%20in%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20capital%20resulted%20in%20significant%20financial%20losses%20for%20drivers%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20transition%20to%20these%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EObserving%20a%20rise%20in%20conflicts%2C%20incidents%20of%20drunken%20driving%2C%20and%20overall%20dissatisfaction%20among%20drivers%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20rectify%20the%20situation%20and%20change%20the%20public%20perception%20of%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20way%20to%20change%20this%20situation%20that%20occurred%20to%20me%20was%20by%20forming%20an%20association.%20Even%20the%20Police%20had%20a%20bad%20impression%20about%20us%20as%20they%20were%20regularly%20called%20in%20during%20fights%20at%20the%20auto%20stands%2C%20as%20well%20as%20those%20with%20customers%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Dinabandhu%20who%20is%20the%20chairman%20of%20Smart%20City%20Online%20Auto%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20360-degree%20image%20shift%20of%20drivers%20began%20with%20a%20noble%20deed%20%E2%80%94%20blood%20donation.%20He%20donated%20blood%20and%20shared%20it%20on%20their%20WhatsApp%20group.%20Inspired%20by%20him%2C%20others%20too%20started%20donating%20blood.%20He%20says%20that%20each%20of%20their%20actions%20inspired%2010%20others%2C%20and%20since%20the%20inception%2C%20at%20least%20100%20drivers%20donate%20blood%20per%20month%20in%20the%20city%2C%20amounting